	(18,13,2,'POMPEYA',157),
	(19,14,2,'<div class=\"block text border-in-admin\">\r\n<p>Pompeya is one of the most extraordinary Moscow New Wave bands of Moscow. For many years the team has been drawing attention of &nbsp;all real music lovers following the latest trends. Pompeya is a live testimony of how &nbsp;up-and-coming musicians can get onto the big stage right in the beginning of thetheir career. Western-oriented Pompeya have a large fan base both in Russia and around Europe and they are adored by all kinds of publicpeople: from serious music lovers to the inhabitants of intellectual fashion dance floors. Remixes of Pompeya\'s tracks made by gurus of electronic music prove this, from artists such as Felix Da Housecat and Fred Falke to Jimmy Edgar prove it.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>However, the musicians still prefer to move west. Pompeya has been&nbsp; touring around the U.S. for a long time and and now they are back home just for a while, to take a breath before thetheir European tour withand the&nbsp; presentation of thetheir new EP \"Night\", which has already been praised by Western critics. The music of Pompeya is very cinematic, it\'s a perfect soundtrack for the summer with its clear skies and bright sunshine.</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"block socnet border-in-admin\"><a href=\"http://pompeya.com/\" target=\"_blank\">WebSite</a> | <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pompeyamoscow\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/user/pompeyamusic\" target=\"_blank\">YouTube</a> | <a href=\"https://twitter.com/pompeyamoscow\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a> | <a href=\"http://instagram.com/pompeyamoscow\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/pompeya\" target=\"_blank\">SoundCloud</a></div>\r\n</div>',157),
