	(22,14,2,'<div class=\"block text border-in-admin\">\r\n<p>Tesla Boy is a superhitanglophone electro-pop project founded in 1980s by the producer and musician Anton Sevidov. The team\'s work especially suited the tastes of the West, and it is not surprising as the musicians themselves are more interested in Europe.&nbsp;<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>Tesla Boyhave twice have become the best Russian music band according to Lookatme. Once named by Radio MAXIMUM &ldquo;The DiscoverDiscovery of the year among Russian musicians&rdquo;, they have appeared at dozens of international and Russian music festivals, where they shared the stage with Klaxons, Missy Elliott, Royksopp, Placebo, Midnight Juggernauts, Yacht, Suede, Groove Armada, The Hurts and Metronomy. They have regular tours around the USA, Europe, Scandinavia and bear the title of &nbsp;\"the best Russian group for export\". <br /><br /> Tesla Boy create polished to acoustic shine tracks - this nostalgic electric discharge &nbsp;that touches those who care about the era of DuranDuran and A-Ha.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"block socnet border-in-admin\"><a href=\"http://teslaboy.com/\" target=\"_blank\">WebSite</a> | <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/teslaboyofficial\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"http://vk.com/teslaboy\" target=\"_blank\">VK</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://instagram.com/teslaboyofficial\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/teslaboy/\" target=\"_blank\">SoundCloud</a></div>\r\n</div>',158),
