	(31,14,2,'<div class=\"block text border-in-admin\">\r\n<p>Easy M project run up at June 2011, gathering popular musicians and creative people together. The band is playing in nu disco style.<br />Stentorious members constitute the body of the band - popular persons from music world, recently proved the high level of professionalism and creativity by big variety of their own works:<br /><br />Ilya Shapovalov - guitar, composer, inspirer of the project<br />Dmitry Ashman - bass<br />Dmitry Fligershule - vocal<br />Evgeniya Romanova - vocal, lyrics<br />Michael Kozodaev - drums<br />John Scighol - keyboard<br />Vladimir Kakovkin - video mapping<br />Konstantin Alekseev - management<br /><br />Thanks to these people, their spacious interests and music trendiness, the project has succeeded in becoming such an unhackneyed and integrated in its concept. Everything has started as a creative experiment, letting people produce on their downtime. But the activity fleetingly overgrows into serious, substantive project. And it works - real professionals couldn\'t make it other ways.<br /><br />There is no doubt in quality result. The band signed the contract with the British label NANG (nangrecords.com) and records their first studio album at the moment. Full release is scheduled for September 2013.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<div class=\"block socnet border-in-admin\"><a href=\"http://www.easym.ru/\" target=\"_blank\">WebSite</a> | <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/easymru\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"http://vk.com/easymru\" target=\"_blank\">Vkontakte</a> | <a href=\"http://soundcloud.com/easymru\" target=\"_blank\">SoundCloud</a></div>\r\n</div>',156),
