	(33,13,2,'',169),
	(34,14,2,'<div class=\"block text border-in-admin\">\r\n<p>The founding owner of the Mutants Records, producer and DJ John Dahblack has coped successfully with almost all aspects of the music industry during his ten-year career. Now, at the age of 28, the musician is at the top of the dance scene and is preparing to bring out a new album, which is going to be released on one of the most recognizable electronic labels - Ultra.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>John Danhblack works in several styles: deep house and techno for the legendary Kompakt, Dessous, Systematic, Brique Rouge and electro for such giants as Ultra, Protocol, Ministry Of Sound, Defected, Vendetta. At the same time he is constantly on tour performing at the most fashionable stages and festivals such as Tomorrowland, TomorrowWorld, Dance Valley, Green Valley, Stereosonic Australia etc.<br /><br /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block socnet border-in-admin\"><a href=\"http://www.johndahlback.com/\" target=\"_blank\">WebSite</a> | <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/johndahlbackmutants\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/user/johndahlbacktour\" target=\"_blank\">YouTube</a> | <a href=\"https://twitter.com/john_dahlback\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a> | <a href=\"https://plus.google.com/111943330340927588867/posts\" target=\"_blank\">Google+</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/john-dahlback\" target=\"_blank\">SoundCloud</a></div>',169),
