	(36,1,2,'About',4),
	(37,2,2,'',4),
	(38,3,2,'<div class=\"block-text\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>SO GATHER UP YOUR FRIENDS<br />AND COME TO THE VOLGA</h2>\r\n<div class=\"block-item first\">Do we travel a lot around our country? When was the last time we spent a weekend camping? How long ago was it when we greeted the dawn on a riverbank? We are living at high-speed and our life begins today. Right now. Online. But it is so much more important to look forward to see new horizons. This year everything will be just like that!</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-item first\">Midsummer. Fresh air and dazzling sunshine. Secret airfield on the Volga bank. Music that changes spirits. Technologies that will change the world. What else do you need to hear and to see the future? It&rsquo;s so simple. Come and join us from 11th to 13th of July. And believe, you will return a completely different person, an Alfa Future Person.</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-item first\">&nbsp;<img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/upload/content/map2.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"block-item first\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-item first\"><a href=\"/upload/content/map1.jpg\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/upload/content/map1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" /></a></div>\r\n<div class=\"block-item first\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>OFFICIAL PARTNER&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\"><strong>Contactless transactions at Alfa Future fest with MasterCard PayPass&reg;</strong><br /><br /><br />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<img style=\"display: block; border: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/upload/content/master-pass2.png\" alt=\"\" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>At the most progressive worldwide festivals (Sziget, Heineken Open&rsquo;er ect) the contactless technology is the official payment tool, that provides paying for purchases by one touch of special wristlet. ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE became the first festival that adopted this technology in Russia.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Come to appreciate all advantages of MasterCard PayPass&reg; to the main fest of music and technology:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>PayPass is as simple and convenient as cash: just tap your PayPass wristlet on the &ldquo;contactless&rdquo; payment reader and the purchase is paid!</li>\r\n<li>Use PayPass to safe your time: the transaction is very fast. Upon payment of the amount within 1000 RUR, the operation is performed&nbsp; without entering PIN-code and there is no need to sign the check.</li>\r\n<li>Security and privacy: the card never leaves the customer&rsquo;s hands and he can control both transaction and the card during the transaction.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>VIP-ZONE</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">Raised up near the main stage there is a VIP-zone &ndash; a detached tent on a podium with a fine view of the general dance-floor. <br /><br />Advantages of VIP-zone:<br /> - individual bars with a diverse range of drinks and a special menu; <br />- separate dance-floor; <br />- an opportunity to see artists and to be photographed with them. <br /><br />To get to the VIP-zone area you must have a ticket of corresponding category. The price of a VIP-ticket includes one parking place in the parking-area, located at the festival grounds.<img class=\"close\" title=\"Закрыть\" src=\"/templates/_default_/images/tabs.info.close.png\" alt=\"Закрыть\" border=\"0\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>ALFA CAMPSITE</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<p>Detailed information will be provided later</p>\r\n<img class=\"close\" title=\"Закрыть\" src=\"/templates/_default_/images/tabs.info.close.png\" alt=\"Закрыть\" border=\"0\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>OMEGA&nbsp;CAMPSITE</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<p>The Alfa Future ticket permits you to occupy one spot in free camping &ndash; Omega Camping - enclosed zone, which is not far from entry to the festival area. There you can find food-courts, pay shower-cabins, toilets and buy all required necessities.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>One ticket permits you to pitch no more than 4 berth tent. A ticket holder could get wristbands equal in number to the quantity of tent berths</p>\r\n<p>Guests in camping are allowed ( festival visitors only ), but only and accompanied by the camp resident. The camp administration does not assume responsibility for any loss or damage of guests personal bears.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The entrance to the campsite is strictly by tickets and wristbands. Please, notice that organizers shall take no responsibility for tickets that has not been purchased through official point of sales.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Omega-campsite opens on 16th of July at 3:00 p.m.</p>\r\n<img class=\"close\" title=\"Закрыть\" src=\"/templates/_default_/images/tabs.info.close.png\" alt=\"Закрыть\" border=\"0\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>PARKING</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">A 10-minute walk from the camping area we have arranged a convenient secure parking area. There you can leave your car safely and not to worry about any unpleasant surprises when you return.\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\nMore information about parking will be available shortly.\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\nFollow the updates!<img class=\"close\" title=\"Закрыть\" src=\"/templates/_default_/images/tabs.info.close.png\" alt=\"Закрыть\" border=\"0\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>LUGGAGE</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">At the festival we have set check-rooms, where you can rent a locker to keep your personal things. Now you can truly relax and enjoy the music, being confident that you luggage is safe.<img class=\"close\" title=\"Закрыть\" src=\"/templates/_default_/images/tabs.info.close.png\" alt=\"Закрыть\" border=\"0\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>FOOD COURT</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<p>At such a huge event as ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE even food-court, situated in the field-center, boggles the mind by its grand scale, comparable to Olympic venues. Just for three days during the festival last year there were eaten more than 10 tones of food and drunk about 30 thousands of beer.</p>\r\n<p>In 2015 we considered all wishes and now there are 32 food-points with Russian, Italian, American and even Chinese cuisines, and drinks are offered in 11 bars offered.&nbsp; Even the most sophisticated gourmand will find his satisfaction.</p>\r\n<img class=\"close\" title=\"Закрыть\" src=\"/templates/_default_/images/tabs.info.close.png\" alt=\"Закрыть\" border=\"0\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>PIECES OF USEFUL ADVICE</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">In this section we will try to direct you to what is best to take with you and what is better not to bring to the festival to make these three days outdoors more comfortable to enjoy music.\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<strong>1 Advice:</strong> As the event is in the open air, we advise to bring insect repellent.\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<strong>2 Advice:</strong> We recommend bringing along gumboots and raincoats in case of unpredictable rain.\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<strong>3 Advice:</strong> We also recommend not bringing expensive jewelry, just in case it is lost in the grass.<br />\r\n<p><br /><strong>4&nbsp;Advice</strong>: Our festival is more of a camping trip than a club party, so choose an appropiate outfit.&nbsp; Better leave your disigner clothes and expensive jewellery at home.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p><strong>5&nbsp;Advice</strong>: 100% sure you are coming to the festival? Then buy your train tickets in advance.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p><strong>6&nbsp;Advice</strong>: Try to find fellow passengers coming to the festival from your city. It is easy to do in the AFP accounts in social networks.&nbsp;<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p><strong>7&nbsp;Advice</strong>: If you plan to meet your friends at the festival, take time to look at the plan of the territory on our website.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p><strong>8&nbsp;Advice</strong>: Make sure you have enough money on your card, or take some cash with you to put money on your account using ATMs at the festival.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p><strong>9&nbsp;Advice</strong>: Get enough sleep before the fest, not in the middle of it. The agenda is very saturated, lots of events are scheduled for the night-time, and you don\'t want to miss any of it.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p><strong>10&nbsp;Advice</strong>: Schedule your days at the fest so as to have as much fun as possible. Decide on which events and performances you want to go to in advance.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p><strong>11&nbsp;Advice</strong>: Look after your your personal property. To feel comfortable at the festival, we suggest that you should rent a locker. The Contact number of the AFP festival is 8-800-707-23-32</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\nNew tips we will add gradually.\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\nStay tuned!<img class=\"close\" title=\"Закрыть\" src=\"/templates/_default_/images/tabs.info.close.png\" alt=\"Закрыть\" border=\"0\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>',4),
