	(44,3,2,'<div class=\"slider display-at-start\">\r\n<div class=\"container\" style=\"max-width: 909px;\"><img src=\"/upload/content/B42B0811.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><img style=\"display: none;\" src=\"/upload/content/B42B0939.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><img style=\"display: none;\" src=\"/upload/content/B42B1710.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><img style=\"display: none;\" src=\"/upload/content/B42B2792.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><img style=\"display: none;\" src=\"/upload/content/B42B4755.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><img style=\"display: none;\" src=\"/upload/content/DP0A4171.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></div>\r\n<input class=\"auto-slide-speed\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"5000\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"block-text\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>In 2014 guests of ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE festival could find and join in sports activities for all tastes - exciting land and water sports shows, team sports tournaments as well as various master-classes.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Extreme sports stars (skateboarding, FMX, BMX, wakeboard, flyboard and agressive rollerblading) staggered the imagination of our guests with their thrilling performances. World-famous masters showed their best stunts in specially constructed zones of barriers and springboards in the Fun Park.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>People at the festival could learn some skateboarding, BMX and rollerblading stunts under the direction of professional sportsmen and instructors, well-known not only in Russia, but all around the world.</p>\r\n<p>The most energetic ones could take part in yoga, street workout, body combat, balance и jam master-classes or try their hand at beach volleyball, water football and basketball.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>There were 12 sports grounds built on the territory of the fest and anyone could rent balls, frisbees, inhflatable balls and other sports equipment.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Playgrounds</h2>\r\n<div class=\"blocks blocks-3\">\r\n<div class=\"block-item first\"><img title=\"\" src=\"/upload/content/3pic-voley-en.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" />\r\n<div class=\"text\">In the daytime, join championships in volleyball. We will provide two well-equipped functional playgrounds.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-item\"><img title=\"\" src=\"/upload/content/3pic-ball1-en.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" />\r\n<div class=\"text\">Under the gaze of a hot sunny day we invite you to play football on the inflatable playground with refreshing water cover.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-item last\"><img title=\"\" src=\"/upload/content/3pic-yoga1-en.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" />\r\n<div class=\"text\">Our professional yoga instructors will help you to relax and revive. A special yoga program is created to quickly restore your energy after a sleepless night.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>2014 FLY SERF</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n<p>FlySurf is so extreme! Special jet-boots, coupled with a gland, which is connected withwawerunner by a flexible hose.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Professional G-team led by Alexei Khorev is organizing series of memorable performances on Saturday July 12.</p>\r\n<br /><iframe style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: block;\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/7bgAzyRSveQ?rel=0\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe><br /><strong>Schedule of Flyserf show:<br /></strong><br />July 11th 22:00-00:30<br />July 12th 16:00-16:20<br />July 12th 18:00-18:20<br />July 12th 21:40-22:00<br /><br /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>2014 FREE MOTOCROSS</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<p><strong>Free Motocross (FMX)</strong> is a young sport in which athletes perform special jumping ramps, making various tricks and acrobatic feats in flight.</p>\r\n<p><br />At the ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE FMX Show is prepared by the team named <strong>&ldquo;Queen&rdquo; (Vladimir and Michael Yarigin with Nicolay Ivankov)</strong>. You can see this show July 12th (19:00-20:00).</p>\r\n<br /><iframe style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: block;\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/1ow912g_m0g?rel=0\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>2014 WAKEBOARD</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<p>Wakeboard or wakeboarding- it is an extreme sport that combines elements of water skiing slalom, jumping and acrobatics. It is a combination of water skiing, snowboarding, skateboarding and surfing. Festival guests will be able to see a professional demo performances on Saturday and Sunday.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>On the second day of the ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE following sportsman will perform:</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Anton Tkachenko</strong> (Moscow) - is reigning Champion of Russia, frequent winner majority of the competitions in Russia.<br /><strong>Vladimir Lazin</strong> (Kazan) - is a founder of wakeboarding in Kazan. He is also a professional sportsman, participant prizewinner of Russian Championship stages.<br /><strong>Mity Gordeev</strong>&nbsp;- is father of cablewake in St.Petersbourg, prizewinner of Russian Cablewake Championship.&nbsp;<br /><strong>Nikita Gerasimenko -</strong> founded wakeboarding school in Nizhny Novgorod. Nikita is a great sportsman, winner of Wakeboard Cups in Nizhny Novgorod.<br /><strong>Anton Mihaylov -</strong> is Bashkartostan championship winner, sportsman, started wakeboarding in 2007, founder of the school of wakeboarding in Nizhny Novgorod.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/upload/content/wake.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br /><strong>Schedule of wakeboard perfomances:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />July 12th 15:00-15:30<br />July 12th 17:00-17:30<br />July 12th 20:00-20:00<br /><br /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>2014 STREET WORKOUT</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<p>Street workout, in other words street fitness, is sort of popular physical training, which includes exercises on the street sports grounds, namely horizontal bars, parallel bars, wall bars, horizontal ladders and other structures, or even without using &nbsp;them (on the ground).</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>At the ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE you could appreciate professional street workout performances. You&rsquo;ll see:&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Sadkov Vladimir</strong> &ndash; Street Workout World Champion<br /><strong>Sergei Spiridonov</strong> - Multiple winner of Workout competitions and festivals.&nbsp;<br /><strong>Alexander Prokhorov</strong> - multiple winner of the competition on Workout.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /><strong>Schedule of workout zone:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">July 11th 13:00 -21:00<br />July 12th 11:00-21:00<br />July 13th 9:00-15:00</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><iframe style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: block;\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/P-hGl_h2p6A?rel=0\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>2014 FUN PARK: roller skates, skate boards and BMX</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<p>For true lovers of all types extreme sport, including &nbsp;skates, skateboards and BMXs, &nbsp;there will be a special FUN PARK zone at the festival. Newcomers could practice under the guidance of experienced instructors or just watch professional demo performances. Skate, bike and rollers will be for hire, but to experience the whole gamut, it is better to take your own equipment.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>There is also a separate \"chillout\" zone with puffs, where guests could catch their breaths and be charged by DJ Stolica.&nbsp;<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>Guests and instructors of the festival:<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>SKATEBOARDING<br /><br /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Egor Konishev </strong>(Moscow) &ndash; frequently awardee winner of Russian and European competitions (Cliche Event Best trick 2005 (1st &nbsp;prize), Osiris Skate Challenge 2006 (best trick)), universal rider.<br /><br /><iframe style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: block;\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/NMcKdkQmmCE?rel=0\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<p><strong>Urij Renov</strong> - frequently awardee winner of Russian competitions, universal rider, designer of one of popular Globe gumshoes &nbsp;model.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p><strong>Max Laptev</strong> &ndash; street and park skater. &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>BMX</strong><br /><br /></p>\r\n<p><strong>Denis Pavlov</strong> (Moscow) is riding over 7 years, frequently awardee winner of competitions (1st place in Adrenalin Games (2011) BMX Street (PRO), 3rd prize in XSA Backyard Jam (2011) BMX Street (PRO), breakthrough of the year in Russian BMX Awards 2011, Respect of the year in Russian BMX Awards 2010, 2nd prize in THE BOX JAM by UNITED (2011), Highest Bunny hop (115см) in FSB STREET JAM ect).</p>\r\n<p><strong>Anton Astachov</strong> (Krasnodar) is riding over 7 years, frequently awardee winner of competitions (1st place: &laquo;Young Blood&raquo; contest 2010, second prize: &laquo;Rookie&raquo; Challenge 2010, second prize: XSA Backyard Jam 2012 (BMX dirt), third prize: Kazantip &laquo;Z-Games&raquo; 2010 ect)</p>\r\n<p><strong>Alexander \"Kucher\" Nikulin</strong>&nbsp;is riding over 7 years, frequently awardee winner of competitions (Russian Championship 2012, AZOV-FEST 2011, XSA Backyard Jam Dirt and Super ramp in 2011, etc.).<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>ROLLERS</strong><br /><br /></p>\r\n<p><strong>Kirill Galushko</strong> (Sergiev Posad) &ndash; frequent winner of the competition (1st place: ADRENALIN GAMES 2011 in Moscow, the 11th Moscow S3T Contest 2012, Homeplace United Fest 2012, Russian Aggressive Inline Park in 2012, Street Skating Championship 2012, Karelian Jam 2011, Viselovo Battle 2010, 2nd place: China Open 2012, etc.).<br /><br /><iframe style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: block;\" src=\"//player.vimeo.com/video/68939875\" width=\"500\" height=\"213\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Dmitry Tipikin</strong>&nbsp;- is riding over 10 years and frequent winner of competitions.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p><strong>Boris Gaysner</strong>&nbsp;- is riding over 6 years, and he is also frequent winner of competitions</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /><strong>FUNPARK Schedule:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">July 11th : 13:00 - 21:00<br />July 12th : 12:00 - 21:00<br />July 13th : 10:00 - 15:00</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>',6),
