	(50,3,2,'<div class=\"slider display-at-start\">\r\n<div class=\"container\" style=\"max-width: 909px;\"><img src=\"/upload/content/robo1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img class=\"no-border\" title=\"\" src=\"/upload/content/slteh2.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /> <img class=\"no-border\" title=\"\" src=\"/upload/content/slteh3.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /> <img class=\"no-border\" title=\"\" src=\"/upload/content/slteh4.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></div>\r\n<input class=\"auto-slide-speed\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"5000\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"block-text\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h1>Technologies of the future<br /><br /></h1>\r\n<strong>AFP - is a festival of tomorrow, and tomorrow is all about innovations. Last year leading technology companies brought their latest innovations to the festival and gave our guests a chance to test the incredible gadgets.</strong> <br /><br />In the interactive zone everybody had an opportunity to dicover the up-to-date technology: with the help of virtual reality glasses one could immerse into a unique fantastical world, some took part in masterclasses in how to create three-dimensional objects, and a few lucky ones even gained prizes, that were made for the winners on one of the latest 3D printers. <br /><br />In the transport zone guests of the festival could find information about modern modes of transport, sit behind the wheel of an electrocar and learn to drive several kinds of electric scooters. An impressive show with a Tesla coil, creating real lightnings, let the spectators appreciate the true value of electricity. <br /><br />Robots, symbols of the future, became the most discussed and photographed objects. Everyone wanted to have a picture with one of our transformers or talk to a \"living\" robotron. <br /><br />In 2015 you\'ll see completely different technologies and the updated versions of gadgets presented last year. Fabulous scooters, unusual technological fashion, \"tame\" robots and amazing cars, as well as interactive attractions and a gadget show that will blow your mind - all coming this July! <br />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>TESLA MOBIL EXPOSITION, YAKIBIKES AND UNICYCLES</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<p>Lovers of automobile avant-gard could enjoy the park of actual vehicles in the technology zone during all three days of the festival. First of all we are talking about mega issue <strong>Tesla Mobil</strong>, in which guests could not only sit at the wheel, but also take part in the test drive.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<iframe style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: block;\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/cbxpJUWU7H0?rel=0\" width=\"480\" height=\"270\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe><br />Furthermore, for everyone who has been tested for alcohol, sanity and driving license, there will be the possibility of passing test-drive of the latest electromobils, yakibikes and unicycle.&nbsp;<br /> <iframe style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: block;\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/reKGWU6wU7g?rel=0\" width=\"480\" height=\"270\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>VIRTUAL REALITY HEADSETS</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<p>For lovers of thrill virtual experiences there will be 5 new virtual reality helmets <strong>Oculus Rift</strong> at Alfa Future People. It is an extraordinary technology, which is using among others by NASA to imitate virtual walks on Mars, and by Norwegian military to controlled unmanned tanks. Oculus Rift technology became the subject of sensational deal - its company-developer was bought by Facebook for a record $ 2 billion.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<iframe style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: block;\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/n6X2yzwF9Zo?rel=0\" width=\"480\" height=\"270\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>GIANT TESLA COIL</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<p><strong>&laquo;Tesla&raquo;</strong>&nbsp;- is also the name of the legendary electricity explorer. The biggest Tesla Coil in Europe will be installed in his honor at the festival. Those, who are interested, could take a picture literally inside a lightning!&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/upload/content/tes.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<iframe style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: block;\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/SqF3Wp2D_OM?rel=0\" width=\"480\" height=\"270\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>3D PRINTING</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<p>At the Alfa Future People technology zone you could find a 3D-scanning and printing studio. Tenth of the most advanced to date 3D-printers allow anyone to acquire their own three-dimensional portrait-statuette.&nbsp;<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>The AFP partner 3D Plemya, supported by Picaso, is going to bring to the festival technologys, that had conquered minds of millions of people worldwide. Everyone during tree days of the festival could see the work of newest 3D printers such as PicasoDesigner, UP! Plus 2, UP! Mini and others, and to see firsthand the printing of brand logo of the festival, to participate in creating their own 3D models, scan yourself and your friends with the latest image capture technology to participate in the exclusive master classes, work out in the creation of three-dimensional models using 3D pen and much much more.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>In addition, you will have the unique opportunity to participate in the national vote, in which the beat model of 3D printers will be determined in two categories, according AlfaFuture: &laquo;Price \\ Quality\" and \"Innovation in 3D printing.\"<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/upload/content/3dplemya_logo_versions.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/upload/content/3d1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/upload/content/3d2.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>ROBOTRON SHOW AND TRANSFORMERS</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<p>There is no doubts, that high technology zone can&rsquo;t do without crowd-pleasers &ndash; robots! We are planning a great <strong>&ldquo;Robotron-show&rdquo;</strong> with the participation of three dimensions mechanical giant and also exposition of<strong> twelve transformers</strong> which are 2.5 m high each.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<iframe style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: block;\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/ddjlcz-1Xg4?rel=0\" width=\"480\" height=\"270\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe><br /><br /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>',5),
