	(65,10,2,'<p>ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE call centre: 8 800 707-23-32 (Russia toll-free)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>By calling this number, you can get answers to any questions: from cashless payment at the festival to the living conditions in the camp.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Call centre of the festival</p>\r\n<p>8 800 707-23-32</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/upload/content/AFP_call2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"360\" height=\"360\" /></p>',1185),
