	(73,3,2,'<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h1>Frequently asked questions</h1>\r\n<div class=\"block-text\">\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>Why did Alfa-Bank decide to support this event?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">We are sure, that ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE festival will become an outstanding cultural music event of a great significance, at the same time providing high level of convenience for all the guests.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>Activities at the festival?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">The top 10 best DJ&rsquo;s in the world. Exciting shows and performances. The biggest stage in the history of Russian music festivals! Special interactive zone with the latest innovations in technologies. Sports area. Comfortable campsite. Foodcourts. Merchandise production. The festival begins at 13:00 July, 11.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>Can I bring the kids to the festival?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">This event is ages 18 and over with valid ID. Children under the age of 18 cannot enter the venue even accompanied by grown-ups. Security guards are able to ask for documents to prove one&rsquo;s identity (passport, driving license) in case of doubt.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>How can I pay for food, drinks and souvenirs at the festival and what payment methods do you accept?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">Onsite there is cashless payment system ONLY. Firstly, you can pay for purchase using any plastic card. You can use any credit or debit card to pay for your purchase. Secondly, in exchange for e-ticket all guests will get an electronic wristband for contact-free payments via Paypass. This wristband will be given to all the guests as a gift from Alfa-Bank and MasterCard. With the help of PayPass you can pay for your food, drinks and other services just in one touch. You can also refill the balance of your card or wristband in ATMs that will be installed at the festival venue.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>How strict are security measures at the festival? Can I feel secure for my children (over 18 years old, of course), although the festival takes place basically at night-time?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">Security of guests is a priority for organizers. At the same time, we do not want to deliver troubles, forcing guests to wait in line to the safety-control area, that is why the number of door frame metal detectors and check-out spots is going to be as large as possible. We appreciate your cooperation and understanding on security measures taken on the festival. To speed up the procedure of safety-control, please, allow policemen and employees of security service to look through bags, backpacks. Take all the contents, which can trigger the alarm in the frame metal detectors, out of your pockets. Cutting or thrusting weapons of any type, gas-bags, flammable liquids are not allowed. Entry is prohibited with any type of containers (glass bottles, plastic bottles, cans). To speed up the check-up and for convenience of spectators, entrance with large bags, suitcases, briefcases will be denied before the tickets control zone. You can leave them in the check-room. The entire territory of the festival will be covered with infrared security cameras with maximum resolution.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>Will there be an opportunity to rent a sleeping-bag?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">Please, buy a tourist rug and sleeping bag in advance as at the festival venue you can buy only a tent</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>Do I need to bring food, drinks with me, if I am going to spend all three days at the festival, or is it possible to buy everything onsite?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">It is prohibited to enter the venue with food and drinks, including plastic bottles. You can bring as much food and drinks as you wish, if you are going to stay on at the campsite or on the free camping area with your own tent. You will have to leave your food and drinks in the tent/car because the entrance to the festival territory with your own drinks and food will be banned.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>Can I bring my pet with me to the festival?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">Unfortunately, you have to leave your pet at home. This is primarily due to the fact that it can simply get lost at the festival or frightened by the loud sounds and crowds of people. Please, leave your pet at home.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>Is there a place at the festival for valuables and documents?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">Yes, before the ticket-control and safety-control zones we set check-rooms, where you can leave valuables and documents for entire festival.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>Will there be wi-fi at the festival?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">Yes, Wi-Fi-points, giving you the opportunity to connect to the Internet, will be installed throughout the festival.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>Will there be a shower at the festival?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">Yes, there will be free shower, located on the campsite. Shower is available for everybody, who buy a tent in the camp.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>How can I navigate at the festival? For example, a tent camp?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">For your convenience, we have created a detailed plan of the territory, where all points and areas are marked. You can take a look at the plan in the &ldquo;Venue map&rdquo; in the section &ldquo;About&rdquo;.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>TICKETS</h2>\r\n<div class=\"block-text\">\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>Where can I buy tickets to ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE festival?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">You can buy tickets at kassir.ru &ndash; the official ticket outlet of the festival. Tickets will be sold as from Tuesday, April 8. We do recommend not to put off the purchase of the tickets, because the number of tickets is limited, and it&rsquo;s important to mention that the price of ticket can grow up by the beginning of the festival.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>Can I buy the ticket on the website of the festival?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">To buy the ticket on the website of the festival push the button \"Tickets\" on the main page and link to the website of our ticket outlet kassir.ru. There you can choose the way of payment and buy the ticket.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>Ticket categories and pricing.</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\"><em>Attention, the information is valid until April, 30. After that the information will be renewed.</em><br /> Ticket of \"Standard\" category is valid thoughout the festival and allows entrance/exit any time as often as you need.<br /> Special offer for \"Standard\" ticket is 2000 rubles. Limited number of tickets is available. <br /><br /> VIP-ticket is valid for all festival days and allows entrance/exit any time as often as you need. The ticket gives you access to the VIP area, with separate bars and the dance floor located on the podium near the main stage.<br /> VIP-ticket includes parking on the territory of the festival. Special offer for VIP ticket is 8000 rubles. Limited number of tickets is available.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>Is the ticket valid for all days of the festival? If I arrive and then go home, can I return to the festival?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">Ticket of any category is valid all days of the festival from 11 to 13 of July without any limitations. You can leave and return to the territory at all times, for example, the following day. Each resident will get a unique wristband, providing all-time access to the festival area. If you buy a ticket on the website of the official ticket outlet of the festival kassir.ru or its partners, we recommend to leave valid personal information: your name and surname, mobile number, e-mail. If electronic wristband is lost or spoiled, reliable personal information allows to receive a new wristband at the festival information centre.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>I am not sure what day of the festival I will arrive. Can I buy a ticket onsite?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">Yes, you can. In front of the entrance to the festival there will be ticket offices, where you can buy a ticket of any category, and also a pass to the camping or parking. But taking into account great interest to the event, we cannot provide a 100% guarantee that tickets will be available. So, we recommend to purchase tickets in advance. Besides, the price of the ticket may grow up.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>I have bought an electronic ticket but have forgotten its hard copy at home, can I print it out on site?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">If you bought the ticket using services of the official ticket outlet kassir.ru or its partners, you can use your smartphone to show the ticket and to have the barcode scanned; you can also print out your ticket in a special place near the ticket control area. Remember that organizers of the event are not responsible for the tickets that are sold by an operator other than authorized reseller or for tickets bought privately.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>HOW TO GET HERE</h2>\r\n<div class=\"block-text\">\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>Which is the best way to get to the festival?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">You can find detailed descriptions of routes from key cities to the festival by car or public transport in the section of the site \"How to get here: transportation guide\". There are also all directions and Google maps with paved routes.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>Which transport can be used to get to the venue of the festival?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">Residents from Nizhny Novgorod can reach the venue of the festival: <br />- by train from Moscow Railway station, Zavolzhskoye direction to the station Bolshoe Kozino; <br />- by taxi; Residents from Moscow can reach the venue of the festival: <br />- by any train, that goes to Nizhny Novgorod or passes through it. All trains make stop on the station &ldquo;Dzerzhinsk&rdquo; short of Nizhny Novgorod. The stop of special free pass shuttles (buses) and official taxi will be organized on that station. We advise to all of the residents, heading for the festival from Moscow (or via Moscow), to take high-speed train \"Lastochka\". This train departs from Kursky railway station and makes stop at the station &ldquo;Dzerzhinsk&rdquo;, time in the train is 4 hours. Because of limited number of places in train, it is better to buy a ticket to \"Lastochka\" or to the other train right after you purchased a ticket to the festival. Residents of Moscow and other cities can put up at hotels of Nizhny Novgorod and go to the festival by taxi, shuttle or trains leaving from Moscow railway station. Residents of Vladimir, Kovrov and other settlements located between Moscow and Nizhny Novgorod, can use the same train from Moscow, or a bus, if there is a big company to come.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>Is it possible to come to the festival on private vehicles?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">Yes, it is possible, but if you have a ticket of \"Standard\" category, you need to buy a parking ticket on-site or avail of free unguarded parking, which is in 15-20 minutes from the festival. Residents of Nizhny Novgorod are recommended to come up to the opening of the festival on Friday July 11 to 13:00, to avoid traffic jams, or to use the train.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>BRACELET - PAY PASS</h2>\r\n<div class=\"block-text\">\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>In exchange for a ticket at the festival I got a bracelet, what is it for?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">The bracelet serves as your pass to the festival. It can also be used to pay for purchases at the festival (food, drinks, souvenirs etc), due to PayPass contactless payment method. The bracelet has a built-in smart-card to make payments. We recommend to handle the bracelet accurately &ndash; it is not only electronic money, but also a pass to entrance/exit the festival area. Do not expose the bracelet to mechanical stress and keep it away from water!</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>Where and how can I get a bracelet, which I can use for payment at the selling spots of the festival?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">All spectators, who pass through ticket control zone and security zone, are given at special spots a welcome-pack which includes also a bracelet. If you have not received it, you definitely will be reminded of this, because further movement around the territory of the festival is simply impossible without a bracelet. When you receive a bracelet, consultants can answer all your questions on how to use the bracelet, and a further detailed instruction is included in the welcome-pack.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>In exchange for a ticket to the event ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE I got a WELCOME-PACK / set with a map and a bracelet. What is it for and how can I use it?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">Welcome-Pack includes:<br />- a bracelet with built-in smart-card (with zero balance) for PayPass contactless payment. The bracelet can be used to pay for purchases at the festival (food, drinks, souvenirs etc.) and to enter/leave the festival. To pay with bracelet you need to tap it to the payment terminal MasterCard PayPass.<br />- unembossed card with a chip (with zero balance)<br />- PIN-code both for card and bracelet (it is necessary to pay for purchases over 1000 rubles)<br />- Instruction on using card and bracelet</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>How can I use the bracelet and the card?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">First, it is necessary to refill the balance of card or bracelet. To do that, use cash-in ATMs, located at the festival territory.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>What is PayPass, what benefits does it give to me?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">MasterCard is a contactless payment method, that lets owners of MasterCard PayPass make purchases just by tapping your card or device (bracelet) at the payment terminal. The card has a built-in microchip with antenna, due to which the signal of transaction is transmitted at a short distance without direct contact of the card and card reader.<br /><br />You do not have to let the card (bracelet) out of hands, give it to the seller or insert it into the terminal. It is enough to bring a card (bracelet) to the terminal reading field to exchange data. You will hear the beep, that testify completion of the operation and you can go on - the payment is made.<br /><br />Attention! If the transaction sum does not exceed 1,000 rubles, entering PIN-code is not required. If the purchase price is above 1000 rubles, it is necessary to enter the PIN-code or sign a receipt (slip). At points where the MasterCard PayPass terminal has not been installed yet, the payment is made with a magnetic strip or chip (depending on settings of a terminal).</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>Can I avoid using card/bracelet, and pay for purchases in cash at the festival?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">No. Cashless payment is the only possible way to make a purchase at the festival. But you can use your own plastic cards.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>PLASTICK-CARD</h2>\r\n<div class=\"block-text\">\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>Can I use my plastic card if it is not issued by Alfa bank?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">Yes, you can. At the festival plastic cards of any bank will be accepted.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>Where can I make aware of the terms of service of the card I received at the festival?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">Agreement on the issuing and servicing ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE cards is available on the Alfa-Bank&rsquo;s website in the section &ldquo;Offer contract&rdquo;.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>Can I use the card and wristband after the festival?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\"><em>Yes, you can. Card (and wristband) expires 3&nbsp;months&nbsp;after it was issued. The date of issue is shown on the front of the card.</em></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>Which restrictions on card exist?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">The Bank sets the limits on the following transactions: <br />Purchase payment (goods and services): 15&nbsp;000 rubles is the maximum amount for a single purchase, with the limit of 15&nbsp;000 rubles for monthly spendings.<br /> 150 operations is the maximum number of all transactions within one month (including refilling, payment, repayment per month). <br />Refilling of the card: 15 000 rubles is the maximum balance of the card in any time. 15 000 rubles is maximum amount of a single refilling transaction, regardless the way of refilling.<br />15&nbsp;000 rubles is the maximum amount of all refill-transactions per month.<br /> The Bank can decline the transaction if the operation is prohibited by the bank policy (for example, suspicion of cheating) or because of the lack of technical capability of transaction at a time.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>If I am not a Bank-client, how can I get this card?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">To receive the card it is enough to buy a ticket to the festival ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE. On site after showing your ticket you will get the free-of-charge WELCOME-PACK including the card.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>Can I share my card with anybody?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">No. The card should be used only by a card holder, whose signature is on the back side of the card.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>What should I do, if the balance is incorrect after a transaction?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">Please contact our call center. Be prepared to provide the operator with the following information: <br />&bull; full card number&nbsp; <br />&bull; card expiry date&nbsp; <br />&bull; client\'s phone number <br />&bull; information on the last card transaction. The solution of the problem depends on the reasons, for example: <br />&bull; purchase transactions: in case if you have forgotten your previous operations, the operator will remind you which payments were made ??on the card. <br />&bull; &ldquo;duplication&rdquo; of transaction amount: the amount blocked will be automatically unlocked in 45 days after authorization <br />&bull; No claims concerning cheat transactions are admitted (according to Offer contract )&nbsp; <br />&bull; the retention period of authorization is 45 days. If the authorization amount is not written off for during this period - the amount will be unlocked and will be available to the Client. <br />&bull; Refilling operation time depends on the device used for the operation. The money will be transferred to the account within a period from several minutes to several days after you have refilled the card balance. In some cases the period of transferring can take from 2 to 5 days. According to this information the balance can be incorrect because the operation of refilling has not been accomplished yet and the balance is displayed without the deposited amount.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>I have spent almost all card\'s limit, how can I get the last 50 rubles left on the card?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">To get the money left on the card you should transfer it to another card (issued by Alfa-Bank or any other bank). If you haven&rsquo;t spent the available balance before the card expiry date you should apply to Alfa bank department and write an application to transfer this amount to another account. The repayment of the rest card limit is accomplished by transmission it to the Alfa-Bank card or other bank. If there is an available balance by the time of card expiration date, apply to ALPHA BANK branch and write an application to transfer the balance.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>I do not agree with the written off amount.</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">Please contact our call center. The operator will obtain the following information: <br />&bull; full card number&nbsp; <br />&bull; card expiry date&nbsp; <br />&bull; client\'s phone number <br />&bull; information about the last transaction by the card. After identification the operator will define more exactly the number of the transactions made. <br /><br /> Perhaps you have used your card to make a purchase in the AppStore/iTunes/Windows Marketplace/ovi Store &ndash; the written off amount in these stores can include the costs of several products. In this case you should check your e-mail linked to AppStore/iTunes accounts. If you are still sure that the amount was written off incorrectly, you should contact a bank branch for a claim. Please be aware that no claims are considered if the challenged transaction was made as a consequence of leakage of the card details, even in case of fraud.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>What should I do if the purchase sum is bigger than the credit limit allowed?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">The opportunity to pay for goods in parts (partly by the card, partly by another card) depends on the rules of the trade spot. You need to address a seller or an administrator.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>How can I use plastic card for online payments in the Internet?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">To pay online, you need to accomplish the following instructions: <br />1. Enter the required details on the website of the store: your card number, its expiry date, CVC2 code. <br />2. If the store asks for client&rsquo;s surname and address, provide the data. The Bank does not check this information during authorization. <br />3. Save all the confirmation details of the operation, which were sent by the store, including SMS or e-mails.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>I\'ve got money refund on my card. How can I receive the money?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">In this case the available balance on the card will increase by the amount of the refund. If the total amount on the card exceeds the limit of 15&nbsp;000 rubles, the excess amount will be available during the following month. The time of the reimbursement depends on the bank serving the retail and service outlet. If the card is blocked upon expiry, the reimbursement will be impossible. In this case, you need to contact the outlet and find another way to get the reimbursement.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Social networks &ndash; competitions</h2>\r\n<div class=\"block-text\">\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>What social networks have official pages of the festival ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">https://www.facebook.com/alfafuture<br /> https://vk.com/alfafuture<br /> http://www.odnoklassniki.ru/alfafuture<br /> https://google.com/+Alfafuture<br /> https://twitter.com/alfa_future<br /> http://www.youtube.com/alfafuture<br /> http://instagram.com/alfafuturepeople</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>Do I have a chance to get a free ticket to the festival by taking part in the competition?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">Yes, you do. We are planning to announce a great number of competitions on three social networks: VK, Facebook and Odnoklassniki.<br /> Follow the information on official pages of the festival.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>Is the prize fund of the same competitions in different social networks combined or separate?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">There are a certain number of prizes for each social network. The participant who wins two or more equal competitions on different social platforms can get only one prize.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>What other prizes can be obtained by participating in competitions on the social networks?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">There are both free tickets to the festival and branded souvenirs among prizes.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>What information is going to be announced in social networks?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">You can find full information about invited artists, prices for tickets, festival infrastructure, transfer, sport and water activities, technology zone etc. on the official pages of the festival.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>Is it enough to keep track of updates on the official pages of the festival ALFA FTURE PEOPLE to receive full information about it?</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">Yes, all information on organization of the festival, invited performers, festival infrastructure, sport and water activities, technology and lounge zones will be fully delivered on social networks.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>',3),
