	(84,14,2,'<div class=\"block text border-in-admin\">\r\n<p>Paul Oakenfold is a worldwide famous producer and DJ, whose tracks can be heard everywhere: in movies, commercials, on radio, television, and even in video games! Although Oakenfold started his music career when he was a child, the real popularity came to him only in the early 90s, when he discovered a completely new direction in the electronic music - trance.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>Within the twenty years of his resounding success Paul Oakenfold has remixed songs of such music stars as U2, Massive Attack, Rolling Stones, Snoop Dogg, Smashing Pumpkins, Bjork, Cure, Simply Red, New Order, M People, Arrested Development and the Stone Roses, and has released more than 35 solo albums.</p>\r\n<br />Friends on Facebook: 793,689<br />Major hit: Ready Steady Go<br />Views on Youtube: 872,000<br /><br />\r\n<div class=\"block socnet border-in-admin\"><a href=\"http://pauloakenfold.com/\" target=\"_blank\">WebSite</a> | <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/Oakenfold\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/user/pauloakenfold\" target=\"_blank\">YouTube</a> | <a href=\"http://twitter.com/pauloakenfold\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a> | <a href=\"http://instagram.com/pauloakenfold\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram</a></div>\r\n</div>',137),
