	(87,14,2,'<div class=\"block text border-in-admin\">\r\n<p>One of the major discoveries in the electronic music of the last couple of years, ARTY is probably the most famous Russian musician in the world, who managed in a relatively short time to win recognition from such elite of the world electronic stage as Armin Van Buuren, Skrillex, Avicii, Tiesto, Above &amp; Beyond, Axwell, SHM, Dirty South and Porter Robinson.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>The first success came to him with \'Gentle Touch\', \'Get On\' and \'Flip Flop\', which were noticed by the legendary Above &amp; Beyond, who immediately invited ARTY to their label Adjunabeats. This close co-operation is still continuing.This success was followed by the hits \'Kate\', \'Around The World\', \'Trio\', and composition \'Mozart\', which shook the dance floors worldwide - a collaborative effort with Mat Zo. Arty&rsquo;s tracks are played by the best DJs, and you can always hear them at the most popular radio stations of the world. Therefore, line 25 in the DJ Mag Top100 2011 was not surprising for the musician (28th place in 2012).<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>However, Arty has been supported by the army of fans not only for his production. Whether it\'s a small club or an American rave of many thousands- Ultra Music Festival, Identity Festival, Electric Zoo Festival, Fallout Festival and Electric Daisy Carnival &ndash; Arty&rsquo;s magnificent sets have secured his status as one of the most popular DJs of the world. From Canada, the USA and South America to the shores of Europe, Asia and Australia, his talent not only has drawn attention of the new generation of EDM, but has won recognition among the veterans of the stage, and the slogan \'No Arty - No Party\' is increasingly gaining popularity around the globe!</p>\r\n<br /><br />Friends on Facebook: 534,137<br />Major hit: When I See You<br />Views on Youtube: 880,000<br /><br />\r\n<div class=\"block socnet border-in-admin\"><a href=\"http://artymusic.net/\" target=\"_blank\">WebSite</a> | <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/artyofficial\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"http://vk.com/id3491737\" target=\"_blank\">Vkontakte</a> | <a href=\"http://twitter.com/arty_music\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a> | <a href=\"http://instagram.com/artymusic\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"http://soundcloud.com/artyofficial\" target=\"_blank\">SoundCloud</a></div>\r\n</div>',138),
