	(93,14,2,'<div class=\"block text border-in-admin\">\r\n<div class=\"block playlist border-in-admin\">DJ and producer Benny Benassi is widely known as one of the most influential, respected and recognized in the international arena of electronic performers.\r\n<p><br />His ascent to the musical Olympus began with his HYIP hit \'Satisfaction\'. The single immediately took the leading lines in all the major European charts: track firmly settled in the first place of the French Official Dance Chart, the second place in the Official UK Top 40 Singles Chart and the second line in the German Official Dance Chart.<br /> <br />He has played at countless festivals worldwide (Coachella, Ultra Music Festival, Electric Daisy Carnival, Movement and many others) and recorded a series of high-quality remixes supported by such names as Madonna, Kelis and DavidBowie. Benassi was also awarded with the cult Grammy for his exceptional rework of smash-hit from PublicEnemy - \'Bring The Noise\'- this was one of the most remarkable moments in Benassi&rsquo;s career.<br /> <br />In April 2013 at the Coachella festival new single &lsquo;Benny&rsquo;, recorded in collaboration with John Legend, \'Dance The Pain Away\' was premiered. Video for this composition was exclusively presented in the electronic version of the Rolling Stone Magazine a little later.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>There are rumors that in 2014 Benny Benassi is going to release a new and undeniably resonant album, the first single of which will be available this summer!<br /><br /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block socnet border-in-admin\"><a href=\"http://www.bennybenassi.com/\" target=\"_blank\">WebSite</a> | <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/bennybenassi\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/user/bennybenassitv\" target=\"_blank\">YouTube</a> | <a href=\"http://twitter.com/bennybenassi\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a> | <a href=\"http://instagram.com/iambennyb\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"http://soundcloud.com/benny-benassi\" target=\"_blank\">SoundCloud</a></div>\r\n</div>',164),
