	(96,14,2,'<div class=\"block text border-in-admin\">\r\n<p>He was the first to confirm his participation in the festival AFP, he is 24, he is from Sweden, his nickname is Avicii and he is coming to us! Avicii will perform at the main stage Alfa Future People!<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>It is hard to imagine that today&rsquo;s best DJ began his career with the remix of a simple song from a video game, but that\'s how it was: taking the track from \'Lazy Jones\' as a basis, artist created his first single \'Lazy Lace\' and published it in the label Strike Recordings. However, the breathtaking story of Avicii began in 2010, with blowing the musical world up with singles \'Seek Bromance\' and \'My Feelings For You\', and also HYIP remixes of Tiesto, Robyn, David Guetta and Bob Sinclar. The first release of the musician, \'Street Dancer\' (2011), stayed on top of the world famous chart Beatport&rsquo;s for quite a long time.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>Among the highlights of Avicii&rsquo;s career there are multi-platinum selling anthem of global EDM, \'LE7ELS\'; 150 million views on Youtube; Grammy nomination for the track \'Sunshine\', recorded with David Guetta; cooperation with world-renowned Ralph Lauren fashion house: Avicii is the first performer who has become the face of the brand in its history; numerous appearances as a headliner at the world\'s biggest festivals - Ultra Music Festival, Coachella, Lollapalooza, Mystery land, Austin City Limits, Exit Festival, Creamfields, Stereosonic, Tomorrowland.</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\nFriends on Facebook: 11,196,009<br />Major hit: Wake Me Up<br />Views on Youtube: 270,000,000<br /><br />\r\n<div class=\"block socnet border-in-admin\"><a href=\"http://avicii.com/\" target=\"_blank\">WebSite</a> | <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/avicii\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/user/aviciideo\" target=\"_blank\">YouTube</a> | <a href=\"http://twitter.com/avicii\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a> | <a href=\"http://instagram.com/avicii\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram</a> |</div>\r\n</div>',141),
