	(100,3,2,'<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h1>Accommodation<img class=\"bonus safit left\" src=\"/templates/_default_/images/safit.png\" alt=\"\" /><img class=\"bonus safit right\" src=\"/templates/_default_/images/safit.png\" alt=\"\" /></h1>\r\n<div class=\"block-text\">\r\n<h2 style=\"background: none;\">Hotels, hostels and private apartment in Nizhny Novgorod</h2>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>HOTELS</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">There are more than 70 hotels of different levels and classes in Nizhny Novgorod. We invite you to make your choice online at <a href=\"http://101hotels.ru\" target=\"_blank\">101hotels.ru</a>.\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\nThis website contains the most comprehensive list of hotels available in Nizhny Novgorod.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>HOSTELS</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">В Нижнем Новгороде около десятка хостелов.\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\nThere are about a dozen hostels available in Nizhny Novgorod. You can find the full list of hostels and mini-hotels that are on offer in Nizhny Novgorod at <a href=\"http://ostrovok.ru\" target=\"_blank\">ostrovok.ru</a>.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>PRIVATE SECTOR</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\"><a href=\"http://nn.sutochno.ru\" target=\"_blank\">Nn.sutochno.ru</a> - на этом сайте вы можете найти самый полный список сдающихся комнат и квартир в Нижнем Новгороде.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>CAMPSITE</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\">There is a comfortable Alfa-campsite with pre-pitched tents. Each of them contains 2 sleeping bags and 2 ground pads, which you can take home after the festival. Camping is situated at the guarded territory, where you also can find free shower cabins, charging points for mobile devices, free Wi-Fi and drinking water sources.<br />One ticket includes accommodation for two persons in a tent, wristlets for entering the campsite (one or two, depending on number of guests in the tent). Inviting gests is allowed only from along festival visitors and accompanied by camp resident.<br /> <br />Fire-arms, any self-defence weapon, pepper sprays, gas mixture, flammable liquids and any glass bottles are not allowed on the campsite. Open flames- fires, charcoal grills, petroleum-lams, gas-burners are also forbidden.<br />No animals are allowed in the campground. <br /><br />Campers are expected to behave in a manner that is courteous to other campers. No entry for alcohol or drug intoxicated people. Persons infringing on the rules will be dislondged from the campgrounds without cash compensation for the ticket.<br />Please, pay attention, that camp-ticket doesn&rsquo;t permit you access to the festival grounds. Every guest need to buy an entry ticket of &ldquo;Standart&rdquo; or &ldquo;VIP&rdquo; category to enter the Alfa Future fest.<br /> <br />Alfa-campsite opens on 17th of July at 9:00 a.m.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>',8),
