	(105,14,2,'<div class=\"block text border-in-admin\">\r\n<p>He is one of the most creative Russian DJs of the last decade. Leading music industry figure and fashion symbol, he is also one of the outstanding figure in the music industry and a fashion-symbol one of the most successfully touring DJs according to Time Out magazine (2011), winner in the category Best DJ at Night Life Awards (2008), and as well a founder and owner of two music labels -Heartbeat Records (2012) and Natural Selection (2003).<br /> <br />Short time ago Alexey Romeo have released the series of tracks &ldquo;Dominator&rdquo;, &ldquo;Boom&rdquo;, &ldquo;Tumblr&rdquo;, which were supported by Paul Oakenfold, David Guetta, Tiesto, Afrojack, Alex Gaudino, Swanky Tunes, EDX and many others.</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"block socnet border-in-admin\"><a href=\"http://alexeyromeo.com/\" target=\"_blank\">WebSite</a> | <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/DJAlexeyRomeo\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/user/romeoalexey\" target=\"_blank\">YouTube</a> | <a href=\"http://twitter.com/alexeyromeo\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a></div>\r\n</div>',142),
