	(108,14,2,'<div class=\"block text border-in-admin\">\r\n<p>With regard to popular passion this blue-eyed blond have has left behind the majority of his star colleagues. It seems that there is no such music site in the world, which that James Zabiela won&rsquo;t be filled to capacity during DJ performance!<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>For just a little more than ten years, James has collected lot&rsquo;s of awards: the status of \'Best International DJ\', \'Best of British\', and the upper places of the main DJ Ranking on the Earth - DJ Mag Top 100.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>Keen understanding and passion for electronic music forced him to improve constantly the technicality of his work, both in studio and during live performances. So it is not surprising that the Japanese engineers Pioneer, started to develop their latest cd-mixers, turned to James. Zabiela helped Pioneer in the development of the their latest models, the CDJ-2000 and the CDJ-900.<br /> <br />In the international music community artist rightfully earned the title of one of the most technical DJs. With each performance musician breaks the boundaries of music perception and laid out \"in full.\"</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\nFriends on Facebook: 264,388<br /> Major hit: Blame<br /> Major hit: 250,000\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"block socnet border-in-admin\"><a href=\"http://jameszabiela.com/\" target=\"_blank\">WebSite</a> | <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/jameszabiela\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/user/jameszabiela\" target=\"_blank\">YouTube</a> | <a href=\"http://twitter.com/jameszabiela\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a> | <a href=\"http://instagram.com/jameszabiela\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"http://myspace.com/jameszabiela\" target=\"_blank\">mySpace</a></div>\r\n</div>',144),
