	(111,14,2,'<div class=\"block text border-in-admin\">\r\n<div class=\"block playlist border-in-admin\">Owner of six Grammy Awards, he enters at TOP 10 of the highest paid DJs according to Forbes, a workaholic and an experienced melomaniac, DJ, who turns his performance into an unforgettable show with a unique, punching to the backbone sound and perfect production - all of this embodied in Skrillex, one of the most famous music producers in the world.<br /> <br />Among other issues, Skrillex is known by for producing a few tracks from the tenth studio album of the Aamerican band Korn &ndash; &ldquo;Path Of Totality&rdquo; - he wrote the lead single of for this plate &ndash; &ldquo;Get Up!&rdquo;. Skrillex performed on the most relevant and big festivals (Ultra Music Festival, Coachella, etc.), bears the palm on Billboard and have has millions of fans and followers around the world.<br /> <br />In March 2014 Skrillex has released his debut album, &ldquo;Recess&rdquo;, which has instantly topped the world charts, including first place in the prestigious Billboard Dance/Electronic Albums Chart, thus repeating the story of his EP Bangarang, which in 2012 has also becaome a hit on Billboard.<br /><br /></div>\r\n<div class=\"block socnet border-in-admin\"><a href=\"http://alientalk.skrillex.com/\" target=\"_blank\">WebSite</a> | <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/skrillex\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/user/TheOfficialSkrillex\" target=\"_blank\">YouTube</a> | <a href=\"http://twitter.com/skrillex\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a> | <a href=\"http://instagram.com/skrillex\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"http://myspace.com/skrillex\" target=\"_blank\">mySpace</a></div>\r\n</div>',145),
