	(113,13,2,'NERO',154),
	(114,14,2,'<div class=\"block text border-in-admin\">\r\n<p>British electronic project, which received his first Grammy for the remix of Skrillex track &ldquo;Promises&rdquo; in February 2013.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>In 2010 Nero won the prize of Beatport as the best dubstep project and the duet started to work on its first album, that was released in summer 2011 and sold in 200,000 copies, and some separate singles &ndash; in more than 800,000 copies, thus becoming &ldquo;Gold Record&rdquo;.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>In the same year Den and Joy from Nero took part in recording the unique dubsteb-symphony &ldquo;Symphony 2808&rdquo;, in collaboration with Philharmonic orchestra of British Broadcasting Corporation (BBC).</p>\r\n<p>For today Nero has released 7 singles and made over 20 remixes with Daft Punk, Beyonc&eacute;, Justice and other stars of the world stage.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>Furthermore Nero can be also heard in the best films of our time: for example, in May 2013 the team recorded the soundtrack &ldquo;Into The Past\'&rdquo; to well-known film &ldquo;The Great Gatsby&rdquo; by Baz Luhrmann. And in 2014 Nero produced the new track of for Muse &ndash; &ldquo;Follow Me&rdquo;.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>Friends on Facebook: 1,577,375</p>\r\nMajor hit: PROMISES<br /> Views on Youtube: 29,000,000<br /><br />\r\n<div class=\"block socnet border-in-admin\"><a href=\"http://www.thisisnero.com/\" target=\"_blank\">WebSite</a> | <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/nero\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/user/NeroOfficial\" target=\"_blank\">YouTube</a> | <a href=\"http://twitter.com/NeroUK\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a> | <a href=\"http://instagram.com/nero\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"http://soundcloud.com/nero\" target=\"_blank\">SoundCloud</a></div>\r\n</div>',154),
