	(118,10,2,'<p>Special offer for the campsite ticket is 5000 rubles for all 3 days of the festival. The price includes well-equipped tent Quechua with high quality rugs and sleeping bags which you can take home after the festival. You can also enjoy conveniences of functional camping, including a modern shower room. There will be one thousand of tents on guarded camping grounds. To those who will arrive with their own tents special places in the separate camping area will be provided.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Special price for a pass to the&nbsp; guarded car park located onsite is 2500 rubles for all 3 days of the festival. The parking pass allows you to enter/exit the parking area any time as often as you need.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>You can also leave your car on the unguarded free parking which is in 30-40 minutes walk from the festival venue. If you are going to leave you car at this parking, you can make use of official taxi services to get to the festival.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The number of tickets&nbsp; available at a special price is limited.&nbsp;You are welcome to make all necessary reservations at the best price now on&nbsp; www.kassir.ru.&nbsp;</p>',1187),
