	(423,10,2,'<p>MasterCard PayPass - this contactless technology, that allows users to make purchases with one touch.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>You just scan your wrist band or wrist watch MasterCard PayPass, received at the Alfa Future People festival, to the reading terminal and your purchase is paid.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Check the nearest outlets, where MasterCard PayPass cards are accepted:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://paypass.ru/paypass-locator.html.\">http://paypass.ru/paypass-locator.html.</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>In welcome-packs, issued at the festival, there were also a nominal cards, tied to the included wrist bands and wrist watches. By this card you can also pay for purchases, including Internet, as well as replenish your account balance in any ATM of Alfa Bank.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>More information about MasterCard PayPass technology:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://paypass.ru\">http://paypass.ru</a></p>',1253),
