	(122,9,2,'<p>The founding owner of Mutants Records, producer and DJ John Dahblack has explored almost all aspects of the music industry during his ten-year career. &nbsp;</p>',1181),
	(123,10,2,'<p>The founding owner of Mutants Records, producer and DJ John Dahblack has explored almost all aspects of the music industry during his ten-year career. <br />Now, at the age of 28, the musician is at the top of the dance stage and is preparing to bring out a new album, which is going to be released at one of the most recognizable electronic labels - Ultra.<br /><br />John Danhblack works in several styles: deep house and techno for the legendary Kompakt, Dessous, Systematic, Brique Rouge and electro for such giants as Ultra, Protocol, Ministry Of Sound, Defected, Vendetta. At the same time he is constantly on tour performing on the most fashionable stages and festivals such as Tomorrowland, TomorrowWorld, Dance Valley, Green Valley, Stereosonic Australia etc.<br /><br />John Dahblack with his show will appear on the main stage on the 12th of July, from 22:30 to 00:00.</p>',1181),
