	(125,9,2,'<p>During the preparation for ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE, there is a full steam vote for the best version of Alfa Bro in the official festival groups in social networks. For now the choice is represented by three types of the character - Neon, Gold and Friendly. Which version of Alfa Bro do you prefer?</p>',1180),
	(126,10,2,'<p>During the preparation for ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE, there is a full steam vote for the best version of Alfa Bro in the official festival groups in social networks. For now the choice is represented by three types of the character - Neon, Gold and Friendly. Which version of Alfa Bro do you prefer?<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>Besides voting any participant can provide his/her own version of AlfaBro design.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>Special competition\'s photo-albums will be made of user-created works, organizers and&nbsp; community members will choose the winners, who will be awarded with prizes!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Vote in Vkontakte</p>\r\n<p>Vote in Odnoklassniki</p>\r\n<p>Send your own design: <a href=\"mailto:alfafuturepeople@gmail.com\">alfafuturepeople@gmail.com</a></p>',1180),
