	(130,13,2,'DROPZONE',149),
	(131,14,2,'<div class=\"block text border-in-admin\">\r\n<div class=\"block playlist border-in-admin\">\r\n<p>Dropzone is a new name on the world EDM stage, a collaboration of two accomplished musicians, amalgamating ideas and experience gained from the trap, dutch, dubstep and moombahton music in a new project.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>After 12 years of their solo careerscareer, dozens of releases withon top labels, successful work with Tiesto, Hardwell, FeddeLeGrand and others, two Moscow musicians Artem Silaev (Saint Art) &amp; Alexander Baras (Saint Rider) managed to do an EDM-duet in the end of 2013. Dropzone is going to bring out a remix on the Russian project The W on Mako Records, which belongs to Proxy, this will happen on the 28<sup>th</sup> of August 28, 2014. In addition, although it&rsquo;s quitefor its quiet a short story, the duet has already performed with Modestep, Yellow Claw and Feed Me on the same stage.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Friends on Facebook:&nbsp;5469</p>\r\n<p>Major hit: Unicorn<br /><br /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block socnet border-in-admin\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dropzoneofficial\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/dropzoneofficial\" target=\"_blank\">SoundCloud</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"https://vk.com/dropzonemusic\" target=\"_blank\">VK</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://promodj.com/dropzonemusic\" target=\"_blank\">PromoDJ</a></div>\r\n</div>',149),
	(132,15,2,'',149),
	(133,13,2,'MUTATED FORMS',150),
	(134,14,2,'<div class=\"block text border-in-admin\">\r\n<p>Music fromof these three Estonian guys from Estonia, currently known as Mutated Forms, started by perusingwith pursuering their passion for electronic sound.</p>\r\n<p>Alexander (Zub) and Artiom (G-ruff) experimented with different genres of electro, using all available software. In 2004 they joined with professional DJ Alex X. First success came to the team in 2006, when the owner of legendary label Formation Records DJSS released the track &laquo;My Feeling&raquo; on the label &laquo;World Of Drum and Bass&raquo;. The following single &laquo;Blue Magic / Green Aquarium&raquo; also got the team noticed by trendsetters of the electronic scene.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>Sound of Mutated Forms stretches through different genres: from perfect harmony in such tracks as &laquo;Homesick&raquo; and &laquo;Pessimist&raquo; to euphoria in &laquo;Chasing Dreams&raquo; and &laquo;Time to Shine&raquo;, this trio creates emotional tracks without the use hearts and flowers.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>But don&rsquo;t let facile compositions to delude you - Mutated Forms is no stranger to dirty bass and theirof fresh hits &laquo;Doubts&raquo; and &laquo;Ready When You Are&raquo;. These tracks in addition to remixes for London Elektricity, DJ Marky and Atlantic Records together form a rough idea of the music fromof one of the most interesting bands of today\'s electronic music scene.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Friends on Facebook: 10&nbsp;143</p>\r\n<p>Major hit: Wastegash<br /><br /></p>\r\n<div class=\"block socnet border-in-admin\"><a href=\"http://www.mutatedforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\">WebSite</a> | <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/mutatedforms\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/user/mutatedforms\" target=\"_blank\">YouTube</a> | <a href=\"http://twitter.com/mutatedforms\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a> | <a href=\"http://soundcloud.com/mutatedforms\" target=\"_blank\">SoundCloud</a></div>\r\n</div>',150),
