	(136,13,2,'PROXY',152),
	(137,14,2,'<div class=\"block text border-in-admin\">\r\n<div class=\"block playlist border-in-admin\">\r\n<p>The musician from theof famous Turbo Recordings, label of legendary Tiga, named Proxy is one of a few Russian producers to be generally recognized on the global electro scene. In 2007 Pete Tong called Proxy the electronic breakout of the year, and then Proxy was chosen by the Prodigy as a warm-up DJ at all shows of the team in Russia and the CIS in 2009. Further to thisBesides, Eugene Pojarnov aka Proxy was personally invited by Liam Howlett to assist in recording of the next The Prodigy album. His tracks are regularly played by Justice, Soulwax, Boys Noize, Erol Alkan, Mr. Oizo, A-Trak, Satoshi Tomii, Laidback Luke, and the musician himself constantly performs at the best raves and parties around the world, including Creamfields (UK), Coachella (USA), I love techno (BE), Killer (USA ), Field day (AU), Sonar (SP), Transmusicales (FR), Gatecrasher (UK), etc. Proxy will very soon releases his brand-new ЕР&nbsp; \'10,000 / Nemezis\'&nbsp;on the label of one of the most famous electro-house producers Feed Me - Sotto Voce very soon.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Friends on Facebook: 65 630</p>\r\n<p>Major hit: Dancing In The Dark<br /><br /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block socnet border-in-admin\"><a href=\"http://proxyofficial.com/\" target=\"_blank\">WebSite</a> | <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/useproxy\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/user/ProxxxyMusic\" target=\"_blank\">YouTube</a> | <a href=\"http://twitter.com/proxxxy\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a> | <a href=\"http://instagram.com/instaproxy\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"http://soundcloud.com/useproxy\" target=\"_blank\">SoundCloud</a></div>\r\n</div>',152),
