	(139,13,2,'PENDULUM',155),
	(140,14,2,'<div class=\"block text border-in-admin\">\r\n<p>Pendulum is one of the most far crying from ordinary drum&rsquo;n&rsquo;bass groupsgroup.&nbsp; Attracting attention from the beginningfounding, the band has formed a multimillion fandom just fromfor a couple of years. In 2003 Pendulum released its firstfirs single &laquo;Vault&raquo; on the acclaimed label 31 Records, and it became one of the most noted releases of the year, which received the title of &laquo;The Best Single Of 2003&raquo; according to the Knowledge&nbsp; Magazine. Later the team released its next single &lsquo;Another Planet&rsquo; onPlanet&rsquo;on the label DJ Fresh&rsquo;а Breakbeat Kaos. The track occupied first position in UK National Dance Chart immediately.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>Then PendulumsPendulum music career also was extremely successful: appearances as a headliner on theat Glastonbury Pyramid Stage, second album &laquo;The Silico&raquo; was recognized &ldquo;gold&rdquo; just a month after the release (whichthere were sold 300,000 copies only in the UK alone), performances for audiencesthe audience of more than 50,000 of people, sold out tickets atto all the shows, admiring reviews from Billboard critics, gigs at Coachella, SXSW, Ultra Music Festival, Download Festival and Bestival, two giganticgiant shows, coincided with the release of theirthe third studio album of the team, \'Immersion\', in London at the Wembley Arena.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Despite the fact that Pendulum does not perform live at present, preferring DJ-sets (Paul &laquo;ElHarnet&raquo; Harding and BenVerse), the team areis a frequent guest of numerous European and American festivals, and in August 2013 one of the project participants, Rob Swire, announced the forthcoming recording of a new, long-awaited album.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Friends on Facebook: 2,171,393</p>\r\n<p>Major hit: Watercolour</p>\r\n<p>Views on Youtube: 21,000,000</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"block socnet border-in-admin\"><a href=\"http://www.pendulum.com/\" target=\"_blank\">WebSite</a> | <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/pendulum\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/pendulum\" target=\"_blank\">YouTube</a> | <a href=\"http://twitter.com/pendulum\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a> | <a href=\"http://myspace.com/officialpendulum\" target=\"_blank\">mySpace</a></div>\r\n</div>',155),
	(142,13,2,'BAAUER',153),
	(141,15,2,'',155),
	(143,14,2,'<div class=\"block text border-in-admin\">\r\n<p>Harry Rodrigues aka Bauer&rsquo;s sensational track \"Harlem Shake\" played a decisive role in his career. Released in 2012, \"Harlem Shake\" received favorable reviews from Pitchfork magazine, but the real popularity came to it only in February 2013. Just after advertingadventing a video of the same name, which achieved status of super-meme in the Internet, \"Harlem Shake\"occupied the top position of the Billboard Hot 100 chart for five weeks. And after this signal success \"Harlem Shake\" became extremely popular.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>Baauer has to say for oneself. He has been producing dance&nbsp;<em>music</em>&nbsp;from the age of 13, mostly making house music and electro. One of the first tracks hewas produced a track under the name Captain Harry and played by KissySellOut on BBC RadioBBCRadio 1. Baauer also produced remixes for such musicians as Nero, The Prodigy and No Doubt. In 2012 Baauer signed up to the LuckyMe label and made his debut mini-album Dum Dum, and in 2013 in collaboration with the well-known hip hop producer Just Blaze created the track &laquo;Higher&raquo;, which was followed by joint tour of both musicians.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Friends on Facebook: 193,606</p>\r\n<p>Major hit: Harlem Shake</p>\r\n<p>Views on Youtube: 44,000,000</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"block socnet border-in-admin\"><a href=\"http://baauer.com/\" target=\"_blank\">WebSite</a> | <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/baauermusic\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"http://twitter.com/baauer\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a> | <a href=\"http://soundcloud.com/baauer\" target=\"_blank\">SoundCloud</a></div>\r\n</div>',153),
	(144,15,2,'',153),
	(145,13,2,'DIESELBOY',151),
	(146,14,2,'<div class=\"block text border-in-admin\">\r\n<p>Dieselboy is one of the founders of the American drum&rsquo;n&rsquo;bass movement. He started his music career in 1998 and always kept focus on creating unique mixes during each performance, providing himself a whole legion of fans worldwide. Dieselboy started from underground parties and after a while became the first drum&rsquo;n&rsquo;bass-musician who entered the Billboard with his single &laquo;Invid&raquo; (2000) and achived his incredible award &laquo;The Best Drum&rsquo;n&rsquo;Bass DJ&raquo; at Global DJ Mix Awards and also &laquo;Best International DJ&raquo; and &laquo;Best International Producer&raquo; at the Knowledge Drum &amp; Bass Awards establishingestablished his status as a key figure of the style. Time after time Dieselboy still appears on magazine covers and his tracks can be heard on MTV, ESPN and in numerous computer games.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>An ultimate inspiration for generations of DJs, Dieselboy does not want to come down from the music stratosphere and creates infinite series of new mind-blowing tracks for his fans. His legendary live shows are also a must seemustgo!&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"block socnet border-in-admin\"><a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/Dieselboy\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/user/thedslboy\" target=\"_blank\">YouTube</a> | <a href=\"http://twitter.com/djdieselboy\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a> | <a href=\"http://soundcloud.com/dieselboy\" target=\"_blank\">SoundCloud</a></div>\r\n</div>',151),
