	(149,14,2,'<div class=\"block logo border-in-admin\">\r\n<p>Duet Infinity Inkhave got through lots of bright episodes on the way to itstheircurrent heavy status. The team consisting of old friends Ali Love and Luca C combined different styles and genres from the very beginning.&nbsp; They worked with The Chemical Brothers, Justice, Roisin Murphy and Robert Owens, and today they are &nbsp;collaborating with Hot Natured, Crosstown Rebels and Hot Creations.</p>\r\n<p>&laquo;Games&raquo;, their debut track on the label Hot Creations,&nbsp; based on the bass part inspired by fancfans, made InfinityInk the craze.</p>\r\n<p>The breakеthough of their single &laquo;Infinity&raquo;, which has got more than 10 million hits on YouTube, turned the band to an influential crew of electronic scene.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Being an underground anthem, &ldquo;Infinity&rdquo; hit Ibiza in summer of 2013, and then achieved success across Europe (including first linesline spotsin French and Belgian charts). Today Infinity Ink whip up the best dancefloors touring across the&nbsp;USA, South America and all over Europe.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Friends on Facebook:&nbsp;45 510</p>\r\n<p>Major hit: Infinity</p>\r\n<p>Views on Youtube:&nbsp;11&nbsp;971&nbsp;995 (&laquo;Infinity&raquo;)<br /><br /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block text border-in-admin\">\r\n<div class=\"block socnet border-in-admin\"><a href=\"http://houseofinfinity.co.uk/\" target=\"_blank\">WebSite</a> | <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/HouseOfInfinityInk\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/user/InfinityInkMusic\" target=\"_blank\">YouTube</a> | <a href=\"http://twitter.com/InfinityInk\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a> | <a href=\"http://soundcloud.com/infinityink\" target=\"_blank\">SoundCloud</a></div>\r\n</div>',167),
