	(152,14,2,'<div class=\"block logo border-in-admin\">\r\n<p>Despite his popularity DJ Fresh always raised lots of questions about himself. How is it possible to stay afloat in such an innovative genre as rave for twenty years? How does he manage to open new sides of drum\'n\'bass on an incredibly regular basis? How could underground artist address himself to the new audience without betraying his ideals? Working with the sound DJ Fresh creates the tracks, which engage new audience, keeping the energy of 90s. A perfect example of it was his hit &laquo;Earthquake&raquo;, created in collaboration with Diplo and Dominique Young Unique. Inspired by such beginners as Flux Pavilion, Jack Beats and Dillon Francis, DJ Fresh experiments with dupstep, electro, dutch house and even moombahton, which formed the basis of the hit &laquo;Dibby Dibby Sound&raquo;. In the service record of DJ Fresh there are: introducing Pendulum to world scene, working with top producers and DJs of the world, two million records and single records sold, two singles №1 and five top singles, and now comes a new track \'Make U Bounce\', having all chances to beat sales records. To be continued!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Friends on Facebook:&nbsp;350&nbsp;271</p>\r\n<p>Major hit:&nbsp;Louder</p>\r\n<p>Views on Youtube:&nbsp;85&nbsp;798&nbsp;082&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block logo border-in-admin\"><img src=\"/upload/content/logo_djfresh.png\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"block text border-in-admin\">\r\n<div class=\"block playlist border-in-admin\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"block socnet border-in-admin\"><a href=\"http://thedjfresh.com\" target=\"_blank\">WebSite</a> | <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/djfresh\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/user/Djfresh\" target=\"_blank\">YouTube</a> | <a href=\"http://twitter.com/djfreshuk\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a> | <a href=\"http://instagram.com/realdjfresh\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"http://soundcloud.com/djfreshuk\" target=\"_blank\">SoundCloud</a></div>\r\n</div>',166),
