	(155,14,2,'<div class=\"block text border-in-admin\">\r\n<p>Benjamin Stanford known under pseudonym Dub FX&nbsp;is a talented bitbokser from Australia. He does not use musical instruments, preferring to create music only at the expense of own vocal chords, a sampler and pedals of effects. Benjamin took up music at the age of 14 and in 17 created his first music band. After the record of the first album in 2005, the musician moved to Europe, where he performed in the streets. Then in London he takes a pseudonym DUB FХ. Today, DUB FX produced numerous releases, including \'Live In The Street\' with unique&nbsp;live&nbsp;sound of street performances and as well an updated double album &ldquo;Everythinks A Ripple / RMX&rdquo;, which contains also Benjamin&rsquo;s first studio album fleshed out with the plate of remixes from various producers .</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Friends on Facebook: 585,453</p>\r\n<p>Major hit: Love Someone</p>\r\n<p>Views onYoutube: 19,000,000</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"block socnet border-in-admin\"><a href=\"http://dubfx.net\" target=\"_blank\">WebSite</a> | <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/dubfx\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/user/dubfx11\" target=\"_blank\">YouTube</a> | <a href=\"http://twitter.com/dub_fx\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a> | <a href=\"http://instagram.com/dubfx11\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram</a> |</div>\r\n</div>',161),
