	(158,14,2,'<div class=\"block text border-in-admin\">\r\n<p>Electronic dance music (EDM), mega-legends Infected Mushroom best known as the sonic innovators of the &ldquo;Psychedelic (Psy) Trance&rdquo; genre. Twice ranked amongst the world&rsquo;s &ldquo;10 Best DJ&rsquo;s&rdquo; by the Bible of the Scene (U.K.&rsquo;s DJ Magazine) and with over 14 million hits on YouTube and a #8 position on the Billboard chart, the Israel-bred, L.A. based duo Amit &ldquo;Duvdev&rdquo; Duvdevani and Erez Eisen have created their &ldquo;music kingdom&ldquo; as one of the most powerful in the EDM scene.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>Following a 3-year legacy of success from Infected&rsquo;s 2009 album The Legend of the Black Shawarma. Erez and Duvdev deliver their most multi-faceted electronic album delivery to date in three years--&ldquo;Army of Mushrooms&rdquo; (May, 2012 Dim Mak Records).<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>Adoring fans continue to congregate en masse for Infected Mushroom&rsquo;s 120/year jaw-dropping live shows including psychedelic visuals that lay as the backdrop for enigmatic vocals, hypnoticarrangements, and psy-trippy synthetic rhythms . . . All walk of life gather in attendance for the same reason: to experience Infected Mushroom, the world&rsquo;s greatest Psy-Trance band of the decade.</p>\r\n<br />Friends on Facebook: 1,366,996<br />Major hit:&nbsp;Becoming Insane<br />Views on Youtube:&nbsp;&nbsp;19,500,000<br /><br /></div>\r\n<div class=\"block socnet border-in-admin\"><a href=\"http://www.infected-mushroom.com\" target=\"_blank\">WebSite</a> | <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/infectedmushroom\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/user/infectedmushroomvids\" target=\"_blank\">YouTube</a> | <a href=\"http://twitter.com/infected\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a> | <a href=\"http://instagram.com/infectedmushroom\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"http://myspace.com/infectedmushroomcentral\" target=\"_blank\">mySpace</a></div>',160),
