	(161,14,2,'<div class=\"block text border-in-admin\">\r\n<div class=\"block playlist border-in-admin\">\r\n<p>Few of electronic musicians today could can boast that they have asserted a great of asserting influence over musical scene.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>Over the last 15 years of nonstop working Andre Tanneberger has made an important contribution to the development of the global EDM. Artist plays on tours from the USA to Asia, including the world\'s biggest festivals (Electric Daisy Festival, Creamfields and Nature One), and the residence of the world famous Marquee Club, in Las Vegas, along with Benny Benassi and Paul Oakenfold, adds points to the authority of the this musician.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>On each of nine album, released by ATB, you can feel the presence of his unique, recognizable style. Being not a slave of fashion, he does not pander to trends and plays purely autentistic! Tracks of Andre were appreciated by global electronic industry giants: Heather Nova, Moby, William Orbit, Bossand Swan, Haley, Fuldner, Dash Berlin, Armin Van Buuren and many others.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br /> ATB is constantly working on recording new tracks and remixes. Ninth studio album, &ldquo;Contact&rdquo; was released on Kontor Records January 24, 2014, and soon Tanneberger is going to release its new compilation, which will fully revealed the soft sound of artists tracks, &ldquo;ATB - At The Beach ...&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<p><br /> Friends on Facebook: 1,553,138</p>\r\n<p>Major hit: Ecstasy&nbsp;<br />Views on YouTube: 5 626 774<br /><br /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block socnet border-in-admin\"><a href=\"http://www.atb-music.com/\" target=\"_blank\">WebSite</a> | <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/andretanneberger\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"http://youtube.com/atbtv\" target=\"_blank\">YouTube</a> | <a href=\"http://twitter.com/atbandre\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a> |</div>\r\n</div>',148),
