	(194,8,2,'Beach volleyball at the AFP festival',1194),
	(195,9,2,'<p>There will be playgrounds for beach volleyball at the ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE.</p>',1194),
	(196,10,2,'<p>Amazing news for sport lovers! There will be playgrounds for beach volleyball at the ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE. These playgrounds with white sand, that is specifically intended to play sun&rsquo;n&rsquo;surf games, will be equipped with all necessary sport equipment.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Professional volleyball trainers, attending on each playground, will help you, so beach volleyball will be available to anyone, even beginners.</p>',1194),
	(197,8,2,'Yoga at the AFP festival!',1195),
	(198,9,2,'<p>Yoga association &laquo;RUS-DAO&raquo; is a partner of the festival, which organizes free yoga classes for people of all ages and levels of training.</p>',1195),
	(199,10,2,'<p>Do you want to take to the path of Yoga but don\'t know exactly where and how to begin? Maybe you are practicing yoga for a long time and do not want to make a break even for the time of the festival?</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Yoga association &laquo;RUS-DAO&raquo; is a partner of the festival, which organizes free yoga classes for people of all ages and levels of training. During these engrossing and insightful classes, you will learn more about different yoga practices, pick up doing yoga positions: asanas and vinyasas, explore brethears, practice in meditation and also find out secrets of recitation of mantras.</p>',1195),
	(201,9,2,'<p>AFP continues to examine music lovers in knowing musicians, who are going to perform at the ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE festival!</p>',1196),
	(202,10,2,'<p>AFP continues to examine music lovers in knowing musicians, who are going to perform at the&nbsp;&nbsp; ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE festival!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Rulesaresimple! First five people, who give correct answers to all questions, receive prices. Person, who gains the lead win a ticket to the festival and other four winners get souvenir magnets with symbols of the festival. Those, who take places from second to fifth, could receive their prices in Alfa-bank offices in their city. We will inform you about delivery date later. To take part in this quiz, you need to send your answers on email: <a href=\"mailto:alfafuturepeople@gmail.com\">alfafuturepeople@gmail.com</a> (mention &laquo;quiz 31.05&raquo; in subject line), and to repost the news about this quiz from one of the official pages in social networks (<a href=\"https://vk.com/alfafuture\">Vkontakte</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/alfafuture\">Facebook</a>&nbsp;и&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.odnoklassniki.ru/alfafuture\">Одноклассники</a>). Results will be drawn up on Friday June the 6<sup>th</sup> .</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>1. Where is situated James Zabiela&rsquo;s favorite club and how is it called?</li>\r\n<li></li>\r\n<li>2. This track, inspired by Formula 1, was produced and recorded by one of the participants of AFP in collaboration with creative team of one famous energy drink. What is the name of the track and who is the author?</li>\r\n<li></li>\r\n<li>3. This musician and DJ was reared by foster parents, and his birth parents were&hellip;close friends of the family. Who is he?</li>\r\n<li></li>\r\n<li>4. This AFP participant is a jazz pianist by profession. Once he was lucky to receive the award from the hands of James Brown! Who is he?</li>\r\n<li></li>\r\n<li>5. Nothing about rock is alien to DJs! Even the psy-trance group Infected Mushroom, which seems so far from havy-riffs, did not miss the opportunity to work with the musician from cultic nu-metal band. Who is he and from what music-band is he? What is the name of the track, recorded together?</li>\r\n<li></li>\r\n<li>6. Few yeas ago in California this AFP participant, DJ and producer of Benni Benassi, took part in this quite removed from the music event. What is the event referred?</li>\r\n<li></li>\r\n<li>7. Russia is known abroad by &laquo;brown bear, Matryoshka and balalaika&raquo;. Perhaps for this reason one of &nbsp; the participants AFP, as a matter of fact, is very popular abroad, engaged in playing the balalaika in &nbsp; &nbsp; olden times. Who is that balalaika-DJ?</li>\r\n</ol>',1196),
