	(210,9,2,'<p>Welcome new participants of the sport area! The partner of the festival AFP, basketball club &laquo; Nizhny Novgorod&raquo; organizes two streetball playgrounds, equipped with the latest technology.</p>',1199),
	(211,10,2,'<p>Welcome new participants of the sport area! The partner of the festival AFP, basketball club &laquo; Nizhny Novgorod&raquo; organizes two streetball playgrounds, equipped with the latest technology. Basketball club &laquo; Nizhny Novgorod&raquo; distinguished it&rsquo;s self at the Eurocup this season: newcomers reached the semifinals of the tournament, leaving behind European giants. And now master classes for beginners will be taught by the real stars of basketball. Sport-lovers and experienced basketball players could spend their time perfect and try their hand in playing friendly games.</p>',1199),
	(212,8,2,'BECAME THE STAR OF OFFICIAL AFP VIDEO!',1200),
	(213,9,2,'<p>You have a great opportunity to win the ticket to the fantabulous music open air of this summer Alfa Future People, but also to take part in shooting official video of the event in partnership with the MUZ-TV!</p>',1200),
	(214,10,2,'<p>You have a great opportunity to win the ticket to the fantabulous music open air of this summer Alfa Future People, but also to take part in shooting official video of the event in partnership with the MUZ-TV!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;If you are an active young man or woman between 18 and 25 years old, living in Nizhny Novgorod, or coming to the festival Alfa Future People, and you would like to shine in the video &ndash; just take your gadget and make the most mind-blowing selfie + photo to the full length!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;Even if you have not previously participated in a similar survey, but possess the acting skills and natural charisma - we are waiting for you with outstretched arms!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>You can use any photo effects and also take photos with friends. The only thing that matters is that your photos are bright, inspiring and interesting! After all, those who made best photos will be invited to the second round Casting in Nizhny Novgorod.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Send your photos ( not more than 10 pieces) and a brief summary about yourself to <a href=\"mailto:alfafuturepeople@mail.ru\">alfafuturepeople@mail.ru</a>. And don&rsquo;t forget to leave your contacts: email and phone number.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>See you at the casting in Nizhny Novgorod!</p>',1200),
	(215,13,2,'',171),
	(216,14,2,'<p>The Uchpochmack is a Russian music band, founded in 2013. Participants of the Uchpochmack performed under stage names: Rocket, Bro and Luka. In the visual component of the project were used cartoon characters. The Uchpochmack put out their first EP &laquo;First &amp; Last&raquo;, consisted of such songs as &laquo;Someday&raquo;, &laquo;Mistress&raquo; and &laquo;Lightbulbs&raquo;, in November 2013. By the way, for the song &laquo;Mistress&raquo; the group invited David Brown &ndash; the vocalist of the American band Brazzaville.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The front vocal, sounded very familiar to many people. December 14<sup>th</sup> , Ramazanova Zemfira during her concert, that took place in \"Russia\" concert hall in Luzhniki, admitted that she has direct bearing on the mysterious Uchpochmack. It was Zemfira, who performed &laquo;Someday&raquo; and &laquo;Lightbulbs&raquo; with two other participants of the project &ndash; her nephews Artem and Arthur Ramazanovs.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The Uchpochmack sounds like elastic and sonorous British rock. Music set at the Alfa Future People will be the first appearance of the group outside Moscow, what is, in fact, the first touring departure of this virtual project. For an event entirely dedicated to electronic and dance music, The Uchpochmack performance will be a bright and unusual rock-and-roll accent, appreciated by the audience.</p>',171),
