	(221,8,2,'LIFE LINE FUND IS AFP PARTNER!',1202),
	(222,9,2,'<p>The ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE festival cooperates with the Life Line Fund. Therefore, part of the proceeds from the sale of festival tickets will be donated to the rescue of seriously ill children.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',1202),
	(223,10,2,'<p>Dear friends! The ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE festival cooperates with the Life Line Fund. Therefore, part of the proceeds from the sale of festival tickets will be donated to the rescue of seriously ill children.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&laquo;Life Line&raquo; was established July 1<sup>st</sup> in 2004 as a charitable program. For past 10 years, the fund has raised more than 1.4 billion rubles, and helped to save and return to a healthy full life 7000 of seriously ill children throughout Russia.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>100% of funds are applying for the treatment of children. The Fund pays for high-tech operations and purchase of special expensive medical instruments.&nbsp;</p>',1202),
	(224,8,2,'AFP ON YANDEX.MUSIC!',1203),
	(225,9,2,'<p>We are happy to tell you, that there is a page of ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE festival on Yandex.Music appeared!</p>',1203),
	(226,10,2,'<p>Dear friends! We are happy to tell you, that there is a page of ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE festival on Yandex.Music appeared!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Here you can receive detailed information about the festival, check the line-up and listen to the records of festival participants in high quality online!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>All of this on the web page of AFP: &nbsp;<a href=\"http://music.yandex.ru/fest/alfafuture/\">http://music.yandex.ru/fest/alfafuture/</a></p>',1203),
	(227,8,2,'EUROPA PLUS IS THE GENERAL PARTNER OF THE FESTIVAL!',1204),
	(228,9,2,'<p>Festival of electronic music and high technology ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE proudly presents the general information partner &ndash; Europa Plus radio station. More than 10 million radio listeners of Europa Plus in Russia and CIS could hear tracks of DJ and musicians, participants of AFP on the waves of their favorite radio station and also take part in festival tickets raffle.</p>',1204),
	(229,10,2,'<p>Festival of electronic music and high technology ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE proudly presents the general information partner &ndash; Europa Plus radio station. More than 10 million radio listeners of Europa Plus in Russia and CIS could hear tracks of DJ and musicians, participants of AFP on the waves of their favorite radio station and also take part in festival tickets raffle.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>About Europa Plus </strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Europa Plus</strong> is a number one radio station in Russia* and one of the largest music networks in Russia and CIS. <strong>Europa Plus</strong> is a daily choice of 10,6 million audience and its weekly audience comes to more than 24 million of people*.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Europa Plus</strong> first went on the air on April 30th in 1990 in Moscow and became the first commercial radio station in Russia. For today its regional network includes more than 280 transmitters installed in 7 countries and broadcasting for over 2400 cities in Russia, CIS and far abroad.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>On the airwaves of <strong>Europa Plus</strong> there are best music hits of Russian and foreign contemporary music performers. Europa Plus is a modern radio for young and active people of 20-35 years who want to keep abreast of the latest musical trends.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><em><strong>* TNS Russia, RadioIndex&mdash; Russia (cities with 100 000 and more population.), October 2013 &mdash; March 2014,DailyReach (Mon&ndash;Fri, 06.00&ndash;24.00), WeeklyReach (Mon&ndash;Sun, 06.00&ndash;24.00), AQHShare (Mon&ndash;Fri, 06.00&ndash;24.00) radio stations among 12 year and alder population. </strong></em></p>\r\n<p><em><strong>The method used to measure &ndash; telephone interview.</strong></em></p>',1204),
	(230,8,2,'UPDATE ON THE SHUTTLE AND TAXI',1205),
	(231,9,2,'<p>You can reach the festival from Nizhny Novgorod by free shuttles and taxi</p>',1205),
	(232,10,2,'<p>You can reach the festival from Nizhny Novgorod by free shuttles on the following routes:</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>1) Sq. Revolution, 2a (Moscow railway station), from McDonnalds - Festival AFP area - Sq. Revolution, 2a (Moscow railway station).</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>2) Sq. M. Gorkogo, from McDonnalds - Festival AFP area &ndash; Dzerzhinsk, (square in front of railway station) - Festival AFP area - Dzerzhinsk, (square in front of railway station).</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>3)&nbsp;Dzerzhinsk (square in front of the Railway station) - Festival AFP - Dzerzhinsk (square in front of the Railway station).</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>4) Parking on the M7 (\"Autostadt\" p.Wood Glade) - Festival AFP - parking M7 (\"Autostadt\" p.Wood Glade)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>During the festival there also will be available an official taxi &laquo;Saturn&raquo;. Their branded cars will be able to pass to the territory of the AFP festival in the Bolshoe Kozino village. &laquo;Saturn&raquo; taxi will be waiting for you on starting points of shuttles and at the exit of the festival. Taxi fare is determined by the meter.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>You can call a cab in advance at phone number:</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Nizhniy Novgorod: <br />8-(831) 423-23-23</p>\r\n<p><br />Dzerzhinsk: <br />8-(8313) 36-36-36</p>\r\n<p><br />Mobile:<br />8-920-007-70-07</p>',1205),
	(233,8,2,'BREAKTHROUGH TO THE FUTURE AT THE AFP',1206),
	(234,9,2,'<p>For the first time in Russian festival story science achievements will be the part of performance program, just like the music is! Alfa Future People guests could literally touch the newest gadgets and have first-hand experience with the variety of gadgets and innovations.</p>',1206),
	(235,10,2,'<p>At the Alfa Future People festival the audience interest will be hold by extraordinary territory of modern ideas, technical innovations.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>For the first time in Russian festival story science achievements will be the part of performance program, just like the music is! Alfa Future People guests could literally touch the newest gadgets and have first-hand experience with the variety of gadgets and innovations.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Lovers of automobile avant-gard could enjoy the park of actual vehicles in the technology zone during all three days of the festival. First of all we are talking about mega issue Tesla Mobil, where guests can not only sit at the wheel, but also take part in the test drive. Furthermore, for everyone who has been tested for sobriety, sanity and driving license, there will be the possibility of passing a test-drive the latest electromobils, yakibikes and unicycle.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&ldquo;Tesla&rdquo; is also the name of the legendary electricity explorer. In his honor the biggest Tesla Coil in Europe will be installed at the festival. Those who are interested can take a picture literally inside a lightning.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>For lovers of thrill virtual experiences there will be 5 new virtual reality helmets Oculus Rift at Alfa Future People. It is an extraordinary technology, which is using among others by NASA to imitate virtual walks on Mars, and by Norwegian military to controlled unmanned tanks. Oculus Rift technology became the subject of sensational deal - its company-developer was bought by Facebook for a record $ 2 billion.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>You also could find a 3D-scanning and printing studio at the Alfa Future People technology zone. 10 of the most advanced to date 3D-printers allow anyone to acquire their own three-dimensional portrait-statuette.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>There is no doubts, that high technology zone can&rsquo;t do without crowd-pleasers &ndash; robots! We are planning a great &ldquo;Robotron-show&rdquo; with the participation of three dimensions mechanical giant at the Alfa Future People, and also exposition of twelve transformers up to 2.5 m</p>',1206),
	(236,8,2,'3D-PRINTERS AT THE AFP!',1207),
	(237,9,2,'<p>It is pleasure to say that 3D Plemya, supported by Picaso, is an AFP partner. 3D Plemya is going to bring to the festival technology, that had conquered minds of millions of people worldwide. Everyone during tree day of the festival could see the work of newest 3D printers such as PicasoDesigner, UP! Mini and others.</p>',1207),
	(238,10,2,'<p>It is pleasure to say that 3D Plemya, supported by Picaso, is an AFP partner. 3D Plemya is going to bring to the festival technology, that had conquered minds of millions of people worldwide.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Everyone during tree day of the festival could see the work of newest 3D printers such as PicasoDesigner, UP! Mini and others, and to see firsthand the printing of brand logo of the festival, to participate in creating their own 3D models, scan yourself and your friends with the latest image capture technology to participate in the exclusive master classes, work out in the creation of three-dimensional models using 3D pen and much much more.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>In addition, you will have the unique opportunity to participate in the national vote, in which the beat model of 3D printers will be determined in two categories, according AlfaFuture: &laquo;Price Quality\" and \"Innovation in 3D printing.\"<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/upload/content/3d21.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/upload/content/3d3.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>',1207),
