	(274,10,2,'<p>If you are going to come by car, but for some reason, you haven&rsquo;t bought tickets to the site-parking of the festival, and you have a ticket of &ldquo;Standart&rdquo; category, than you can leave your car at guarded paid parking &ldquo;Autograd \", located on highway M7. Parking fee per day is 100 rubles.<br /><br /> For your convenience there will be shuttles, operating in a loop &ldquo;AFP festival site&rdquo; &ndash; &ldquo;Autograd&rdquo; parking.<br /><br /> Travel directions for drivers: how to reach &ldquo;Autograd&rdquo; from different citys.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Nizhniy Novgorod<br /><br /></strong></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://maps.yandex.ru/?rtext=56.321087%2C43.985702~56.305998%2C43.676466&amp;sll=43.927903%2C56.313564&amp;sspn=1.175537%2C0.329352&amp;rtm=atm&amp;source=route&amp;ll=43.927903%2C56.313564&amp;spn=1.175537%2C0.329352&amp;z=11&amp;l=map\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/upload/content/nn1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Moscow</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://maps.yandex.ru/?rtext=55.796739%2C37.690300~56.305998%2C43.676466&amp;sll=40.798048%2C55.936233&amp;sspn=9.404297%2C2.661191&amp;rtm=atm&amp;source=route&amp;ll=40.798048%2C55.936233&amp;spn=9.404297%2C2.661191&amp;z=8&amp;l=map\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/upload/content/msk4.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Kazan</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://maps.yandex.ru/?rtext=55.791860%2C49.114993~56.305998%2C43.676466&amp;sll=46.596466%2C56.447322&amp;sspn=9.404297%2C2.625843&amp;rtm=atm&amp;source=route&amp;ll=46.596466%2C56.447322&amp;spn=9.404297%2C2.625843&amp;z=8&amp;l=map\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/upload/content/kaz1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Samara</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://maps.yandex.ru/?rtext=53.195500%2C50.102143~56.305998%2C43.676466&amp;sll=47.217244%2C54.643722&amp;sspn=18.808594%2C5.500923&amp;