	(4011,8,2,'TOT:SPOT STAGE',1278),
	(4012,9,2,'<p>We continue to announce the line-up of ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE 2015! Here are the names of the DJs of the third stage, who will please the fans of tech house, deep house and high-quality club sound!</p>',1278),
	(4013,10,2,'<p>We continue to announce the line-up of ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE 2015! Here are the names of the DJs of the third stage, who will please the fans of tech house, deep house and high-quality club sound!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>TOT:SPOT is an exclusive twenty-four-hour dance floor with a unique artistic decoration, integrating the concept of intellectual development and great music erudition. In a short space of time the team of this independent dance floor realized their bright ideas at the 84UDO open-air 2014, Burning ManDecompression&rsquo;14, Pravda club and lots of other projects.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>As part of the AFP festival the stage TOT:SPOT will appear as a fabulous art object, where each installation is a part of the overall design and the single idea.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>So, meet famous Russian musicians, residents of the best Moscow clubs (Arma17, Gipsy, Vanilla Ninja, Propaganda, Rodnya) and DJs of several radio stations (Megapolis FM, Silver rain Maximum):</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>AGRABA / ALEXANDER NUZHDIN / ASAGA / BOYM / CULTKITCHEN / DAN JAMKINSUN / DATAMODE / DAVO / DOP\'Q / DOYEQ / ILYA RICHTER / KORABLOVE / MASHERA / MONOPLAY / NIKITA ZABELIN / ODY ARTS / ROUSTAM / SERGEY SANCHEZ / SERGEY SAPUNOV / STAB 9 / SUMA / YULIA GATINA.*</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>This is only a small part of the surprises we&rsquo;ve prepared for you! New names are yet to come! Stay with us!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>* Names put in the alphabetical order&nbsp;</p>',1278),
	(4014,8,2,'BEELINE at AFP',1279),
	(4015,9,2,'<p>The AFP festival is traditionally supported by our friend and reliable partner &laquo;Beeline&raquo;. It is the fast and modern mobile internet, covering the whole territory of the festival, including campsites, &nbsp;that will help you always stay online and share your impressions of the high points of the festival in all social networks.&nbsp;</p>',1279),
	(4016,10,2,'<p>The AFP festival is traditionally supported by our friend and reliable partner &laquo;Beeline&raquo;. It is the fast and modern mobile internet, covering the whole territory of the festival, including campsites, &nbsp;that will help you always stay online and share your impressions of the high points of the festival in all social networks.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Say yes to snapshots, videos and check-ins!</p>\r\n<p>But there is more to come! There are a lot of surprises and features from Beeline ahead, that we&rsquo;re going to tell you about very soon!</p>',1279),
	(4017,8,2,'DJS Contest',1280),
	(4018,9,2,'<p>Attention! We are ready to announce the results of the competition among young musicians, your talents astounded and surprised the strict but competent team of judges. During the competition we have received more than 800 interesting works from gifted musicians all over Russia, and we are very pleased you have supported our initiative so actively. The choice was not easy, we promise you!&nbsp;</p>',1280),
	(4019,10,2,'<p>Attention! We are ready to announce the results of the competition among young musicians, your talents astounded and surprised the strict but competent team of judges. During the competition we have received more than 800 interesting works from gifted musicians all over Russia, and we are very pleased you have supported our initiative so actively. The choice was not easy, we promise you!&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>So then, a round of applause for our brilliant talents! Here are the names of the winners:&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Adam Antine / Alex Larichev / Anjey / Antonio Next / Антон Маскелиаде / AstroFox / Azystuff / Banghook / Cable Toy / Dancekraft / Deathcrime / DIOKI / DJ Antention / DMNDZ / Dyrage / Iron Shake / Kirill Slepuha / Lick Da Cat / Mil &amp; Systemdo / Mr. Dee / Piramex / Praga / Sound Quelle / Tellur / The Brig / Un4Get / Vedde &amp; Omslag / Vndy Vndy / VOLAC / White Gangster.*</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Hurrah for all of you, guys! The organizers will contact you before the 10<sup>th</sup> of June in order to verify all details. As it was stated before, the winners of the competition will get the unique opportunity to perform at the ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE festival 2015, which takes place from the 17<sup>th</sup> till the 19<sup>th</sup> of July at the aerodrome in the environs of Nizhni Novgorod. The best tracks will be included into the official CD of the festival.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>* Names put in the alphabetical order&nbsp;</p>',1280),
