	(4023,8,2,'TRAIN SCHEDULE ',1282),
	(4024,9,2,'<p>Keep track of the announcements on the information board of the Moscow railway terminal and on the PA system. Volunteers from the festival will be working at the&nbsp; terminal to help you to find your bearings.</p>',1282),
	(4025,10,2,'<p>Keep track of the announcements on the information board of the Moscow railway terminal and on the PA system. Volunteers from the festival will be working at the&nbsp; terminal to help you to find your bearings.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>You can ride the train from Nizhni Novgorod to the festival and back an unlimited number of times, once you&rsquo;ve paid for the return ticket &ldquo;Nizhni Novgorod &ndash; Kozino&rdquo;. Keep the ticket for the train, show it to the ticket checker together with your ticket to the festival (or with your electronic bracelet) and enjoy the freedom of movement by the local train.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>You can find the complete schedule&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.vvppk.ru/kak-dobratsya\">here</a>.</p>',1282),
	(4026,8,2,'MIRODIN AT AFP ',1283),
	(4027,9,2,'<p>At AFP festival we&rsquo;ll be dancing, eating delicious food and testing latest gadgets a lot. Considering the busy schedule, there&rsquo;ll be no time for sleeping, but you shouldn&rsquo;t stop caring about your body. All guests of the AFP festival will get a rare opportunity not only to relax, but to check their state of health as well, and what is more, free of charge! &nbsp;</p>',1283),
	(4028,10,2,'<p>At AFP festival we&rsquo;ll be dancing, eating delicious food and testing latest gadgets a lot. Considering the busy schedule, there&rsquo;ll be no time for sleeping, but you shouldn&rsquo;t stop caring about your body. All guests of the AFP festival will get a rare opportunity not only to relax, but to check their state of health as well, and what is more, free of charge! &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>This opportunity will be offered by the &ldquo;Mirodin&rdquo; Community &ndash; look out for the charming nurses in the health innovative technologies section.&nbsp;Here everyone will be able to learn about medical novelties with the help of a big 3D laboratory, to test for themselves the innovative medical technologies and to combat dangerous viruses in the virtual reality in the lounge zone. There will be a lot of surprises and competitions, and the &ldquo;Mirodin&rdquo; team has prepared really cool prizes for the participants!</p>',1283),
