	(287,8,2,'AFP: FASHION TIPS',1220),
	(288,9,2,'<p>Each festival with a history gradually creates its fashion. Alfa Future People electro music festival will pass for the fist time ever, so every guest has a chance to become a trendsetter. The brighter and more interesting you party costume is, the more likely that it will be copied later. We are sure, that AFP visitors have taste, which distinguishes them, and creative approach to appearance. However, it is important to be sensibly dressed, after all you are going to spend three days outdoors.</p>',1220),
	(289,10,2,'<p>Each festival with a history gradually creates its fashion. Alfa Future People electro music festival will pass for the fist time ever, so every guest has a chance to become a trendsetter. The brighter and more interesting you party costume is, the more likely that it will be copied later. We are sure, that AFP visitors have taste, which distinguishes them, and creative approach to appearance. However, it is important to be sensibly dressed, after all you are going to spend three days outdoors.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>We suggest you some simple tips about how to feel comfortable on the open-air and stay in style.</p>\r\n<p><br /> <strong>Shoes</strong><br /> </p>\r\n<p>In every clothing shoes play the decisive role. Few dare to spend three days on the grass in high heels or in narrow model shoes of patent leather. Avoid also open sandals or slippers, threaten to fly off from the foot. You will have to walk a lot and dance until morning, so the best choice is shoes or sneakers. Take care of your legs and holiday shoes.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Clothes</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Light and easy clothes (loose or not hampering movements), preferably made ??of natural fabrics is better for the festival. Sporty style and smart casual - shirts, shorts, jeans, overalls, skirts is best to put on. By the way shorts and jeans with a high waist-trend of the season.</p>\r\n<p>Avoid skirts of floor-length - they could easily catch something. Evening dresses, sophisticated cut and pantsuits will look out of place at the festival.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Whatever it is warm in anticipation of the event, grab warm clothing in case in case of cold weather. Sweatshirts and hoodies won&rsquo;t take much space in your bag.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The festival takes place on the banks of the Volga, so take swimwear.</p>\r\n<p><br /> At the festival will be a sport area, so do not forget to set light sportswear to play volleyball, streetball, do yoga and fitness with instructors, etc.<br /> </p>\r\n<p><strong>Accessories</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>We suggest girls to take wide shawl or scarf made ??of natural fabric. It will protect from light wind or sun. Headwear is required for all guests at the open area. As well as sunglasses. We do not recommend clutches. Belt bag, where you can put all valuables and keep them to yourself is an ideal choice. Do not wear jewelry: they are easy to lose and almost impossible to find.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/upload/content/shutterstock_20039804923.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>',1220),
	(290,13,2,'',172),
	(291,14,2,'<div class=\"block text border-in-admin\">\r\n<p>KOLYA (Nikolai Danilin) was born May 3 of the year 1976 in Moscow. Now KOLYA is one of the most recognizable DJ in Russia, who entered TOP 10 DJ RUSSIA time and again, according largest music Internet resources, including PROMODJ. His name associates with almost hours of emotional, delish, dance music, and waves of positive, going all over the audience. His rare music taste formed in the late 80s - early 90s. Passion to party and first festivals in Moscow &ndash; these two pushed KOLYA deeper and deeper into the world of club life and winding House. However, KOLYA didn&rsquo;t lost in all that extra-dance and deep-emotional style, but became one of the brightest signature sound creators. To achieve magical sound he carefully chose the music, experimenting with styles House, ClubHouse, VocalHouse, DiscoHouse, Electro, Progressive, creating beautiful musical twists and turns that could not leave anyone indifferent.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;In 2003 KOLYA found his home in the legendary famous Moscow club &ldquo;XIII&rdquo;, where every self-respecting DJ and clubber deserved to come. Together with his friend DJ Grad, KOLYA surprised sophisticated metropolitan audience with precious House, and met such guests as John Digweed, Paul Oakenfold, Sasha, Boy George, Deep Dish, Judge Jules, Steve Lawler, Danny Tenaglia, Sander Kleinenberg, Eric Morillo and lot&rsquo;s of other glorious musicians. It is in &ldquo;XIII&rdquo; the first big success came to KOLYA. During his residency at the club, he becomes an anchor of the popular program \"Dance Floor\" on MTV Live and sparkle the air on the legendary station 106.8 at the same time.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>In 2010&nbsp;KOLYA released a mix on Pacha Records, and was invited to the club PACHA IBIZA, where he became the first Russian DJ played his warm-up in the walls of fabulous Spanish club. In addition KOLYA was music-director of Pacha Moscow from 2008 to June 2011. That time Pacha Moscow entered the TOP 100 of best clubs in Russia.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>For over 10 years and currently now KOLYA leads radio show \"RECORD BOX\" on the waves of DFM 101.2 - best dance radio station of the country. High rating confirms the fact that his long career of disc jockey correctly conveys club segment to people.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>KOLYA still continues to delight his fans with quality electronic music, as well as successfully writes his tracks releasing on best European labels. Among them, the most interesting track with English vocalist Peyton. Their first joint appearance at SWMC 2011 was unforgettable. Peyton then said in an interview that Russian electronic scene is underestimated. As a result of creative collaboration appeared a track titled HOW TO LOVE, which has received support as a remix from Eric Cooper, owner of two GRAMMY.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block socnet border-in-admin\">&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/djkolya\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"https://twitter.com/djkolya\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/djkolya\" target=\"_blank\">SoundCloud</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"https://vk.com/kolyadj\" target=\"_blank\">VK</a></div>',172),
