	(309,9,2,'<p>We are pleased to announce that the food in the VIP-zone at the ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE festival will be provided by the restaurant group La Familia. Festival guests could check a special organic-menu of fresh farm products imported from the south of Russia!</p>',1226),
	(310,10,2,'<p>We are pleased to announce that the food in the VIP-zone at the ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE festival will be provided by the restaurant group La Familia. Festival guests could check a special organic-menu of fresh farm products imported from the south of Russia!<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>La Familia is one of the leading restaurant groups of Caucasian Mineral Waters. Today, the group owns 4 restaurants, 4 coffee shops, 3 canteens and 5 confectioneries. Here are some of them:<br /> <br />&laquo;Soho Lounge&raquo; Club - restaurant it is fine Mediterranean cuisine in the center of Pyatigorsk. Fresh seafood is daily delivered to the restaurant from France by plane.<br /> <br />Restaurant &laquo;Khiva&raquo; is the first and the only restaurant on the Uzbek territory of Caucasian Mineral Waters. All dishes are seasoned with spices that are imported from Uzbekistan.</p>\r\n<p>&laquo;Compania&raquo; is the first classical steakhouse of Caucasian Mineral Waters. In addition to high-quality steaks from 10 kinds of meat, the restaurant serves classic European cuisine and beer snacks.<br /> <br />http://soho-lounge.ru/events</p>',1226),
	(311,8,2,'CHECK ROOMS AND LOCKERS',1227),
	(312,9,2,'<p>Dear friends, for your convenience, reliable lockers will be installed at the entrance to the festival in front of a metal detector.</p>',1227),
	(313,10,2,'<p>Dear friends, for your convenience, reliable lockers will be installed at the entrance to the festival in front of a metal detector.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>You can put inside valuables (keys, documents, gadgets), as well as items that are forbidden to bring to the festival territory, such as penknives. The cost of renting the locker for 3 days is 500 rubles and there is also a key deposit, which will be refunded when you return the keys to the organizers. Number of lockers is limited.</p>',1227),
	(314,8,2,'CAR STICKERS',1228),
	(315,9,2,'<p>Dear friends, in &laquo;Pushkinskiy&raquo; Alfa-bank department in Nizhniy Novgorod you can get an original sticker for your car totally free of charge.</p>',1228),
	(316,10,2,'<p>Dear friends, in &laquo;Pushkinskiy&raquo; Alfa-bank department in Nizhniy Novgorod you can get an original sticker for your car totally free of charge.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The Alfa-bank department address:&nbsp;Belinsky Str, 61. More information about the work of the department you can find on the site of Alfa-Bank <a href=\"http://alfabank.ru/nizhninovgorod/address/pushkinsky/\">http://alfabank.ru/nizhninovgorod/address/pushkinsky/</a>.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Hurry up, because the number of stickers is limited.&nbsp;</p>',1228),
	(317,8,2,'«Vremya N» - report from AFP',1229),
	(318,9,2,'<p>&laquo;Vremya N&raquo; channel spread footage from the site in Balakhninsky region, where preparations for the festival of electronic music and modern technology &laquo;Alfa Future People&raquo;, which will take place from 11 to 13 July, are conducted.</p>',1229),
	(319,10,2,'<p>&laquo;Vremya N&raquo; channel spread footage from the site in Balakhninsky region, where preparations for the festival of electronic music and modern technology &laquo;Alfa Future People&raquo;, which will take place from 11 to 13 July, are conducted.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;The shooting team visited the Main stage and talked to the festival organizers and those who construct podiums and incredible objects in the shape of giant robots, with platforms for performances inside their heads.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The first Russian festival of electronic music and modern technology &laquo;Alfa Future People&raquo; will be held from 11 to 13 July 2014 at the airfield on the Volga River in the Bolshoe Kozino (Balakhninsky region).</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Festival &laquo;Alfa Future People&raquo; is organized by &laquo;Alfa-Bank&raquo; with the support of the Government of Nizhegorodskaya oblast. AVICII, SKRILLEX, PAUL OAKENFOLD, MARKUS SCHULZ, BENNY BENASSI and about 40 of the world elite DJs will perform in the three-day festival program. Best Russian electronic musicians will also participate in the festival. As a special guest you will see the performance of The Uchpochmack, with the following membership of Zemfira Ramazanova.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.vremyan.ru/news/pojavilos_video_podgotovki_k_festivalju_Alfa_Future_People.html\">http://www.vremyan.ru/news/pojavilos_video_podgotovki_k_festivalju_Alfa_Future_People.html<br /><br /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/ehVCkJ9Lp8g?rel=0\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>',1229),
