	(330,9,2,'<p>It&rsquo;s time to sum up results for the contest of young Russian artists AFP, who will perform in the 3<sup>rd</sup>&nbsp;&nbsp;day of the festival (July 13). That was a great challenge for our jury was to choose the best of the best among 250 bold, ambitious and talented members because each of them is unique. But the rules of the contest are strict and only 10 can become winners. The jury made ??its choice.</p>',1233),
	(331,10,2,'<p>It&rsquo;s time to sum up results for the contest of young Russian artists AFP, who will perform in the 3<sup>rd</sup> &nbsp;day of the festival (July 13). That was a great challenge for our jury was to choose the best of the best among 250 bold, ambitious and talented members because each of them is unique. But the rules of the contest are strict and only 10 can become winners. The jury made ??its choice.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>In the 3<sup>rd</sup>&nbsp; day of the festival from 06:00 to 14:00 on the Live&amp;bass stage you&rsquo;ll hear:</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>06:00 - 07:00&nbsp;<strong>DJ ANDREY TOPCHY</strong>&nbsp;(Nizhniy Novgorod)&nbsp;<br /> 07:00 - 07:45&nbsp;<strong>DJ EUGENE</strong>&nbsp;(Nizhniy Novgorod)&nbsp;<br /> 07:45 - 08:30&nbsp;<strong>DJ SEMENOVA</strong>&nbsp;(Nizhniy Novgorod)<br /> 08:30 - 09:15&nbsp;<strong>MOON SUN</strong>&nbsp;(Kursk)<br /> 09:15 - 10:00&nbsp;<strong>SHIZA</strong>&nbsp;(Moscow)<br /> 10:00 - 10:45&nbsp;<strong>EFIM KERBUT</strong>&nbsp;(Moscow)<br /> 10:45 - 11:30&nbsp;<strong>DUNKY &amp; NEVEL</strong>&nbsp;(Kirov)<br /> 11:30 - 12:15&nbsp;<strong>AUDIOCELLS</strong>&nbsp;(Kazan)<br /> 12:15 - 13:00&nbsp;<strong>DIAMONDS BASTARDS</strong>&nbsp;(Perm)<br /> 13:15 - 14:00&nbsp;<strong>KiMURA</strong>&nbsp;(Moscow)</p>',1233),
