	(447,3,2,'<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>MEDIA ABOUT THE FESTIVAL<br /><img class=\"bonus safit left\" src=\"/templates/_default_/images/safit.png\" alt=\"\" /><img class=\"bonus safit right\" src=\"/templates/_default_/images/safit.png\" alt=\"\" /></h2>\r\n<div class=\"block-text\">\r\n<p><img src=\"/upload/content/glean_news_183081.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.vedomosti.ru/lifestyle/articles/2015/11/09/616086-alfa-future-people-priznan-luchshim-muzikalnim-sobitiem-v-evrope\" target=\"_blank\">Alfa Future People is awarded as the best European misic festival</a></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>First time for the 10 years Russian representatives took the First place at EuBEA contest</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><img src=\"/upload/content/muz-tv_11.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"66\" height=\"64\" /><br /><a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UBcO8d-4MEs\" target=\"_blank\">Pro Novosti, Muz TV</a></h3>\r\n<p>Report from Alfa Future People music festival&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><img src=\"/upload/content/HCCPDF8P-9I.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"66\" height=\"56\" />&nbsp;<br /><a href=\"http://www.colta.ru/articles/music_modern/8005\" target=\"_blank\">Alfa Music Festival&nbsp;</a></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>50 tones of gravel, 25 thousand of burgers and one kangaroo or how the Alfa Future People music festival gone&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><img src=\"/upload/content/kom.jpg\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<br /><a href=\"http://www.kommersant.ru/doc/2525264\" target=\"_blank\">Rave on Volga. The 1st music festival has gone in Nizhniy Novgorod district</a></h3>\r\n<p>On an abandoned airfield near the Bolshoe Kozino village&nbsp;near Nizhny Novgorod has gone&nbsp;the first festival of music and technology Alfa Future People.</p>\r\n<p>Report Elena KRAVTSUN and Boris&nbsp;Barabanov</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><img src=\"/upload/content/rg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br /><a href=\"http://www.rg.ru/2014/07/16/zvuk-poln.html\" target=\"_blank\">How to mix modern technologies and EDM</a></h3>\r\n<h3>Technologies are part of our everyday life, and nobody will be surprised, for example, the inscription on the hairdresser \"Do staining in 5D\". But when it comes to the arts, then there is news acquire special meaning</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><img src=\"/upload/content/Снимок2.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"198\" height=\"36\" />&nbsp;<br /><a href=\"http://www.regnum.ru/news/it/1819408.html#ixzz35qqGDYbx\" target=\"_blank\">Near Nizhniy Novgorod will be held the 1s EDM festival Alfa Future People</a></h3>\r\n<p>AVICII, SKRILLEX, PAUL OAKENFOLD, MARKUS SCHULZ, BENNY BENASSI and 40 DJs from the elite world of electronic music will perform in the three-day festival.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><img src=\"/upload/content/Снимок3.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"192\" height=\"45\" />&nbsp;<br /><a href=\"http://nn.rbc.ru/nn_topnews/05/06/2014/928867.shtml\" target=\"_blank\">The biggest scene in the Europe will be built near Nizhniy Novgorod for Alfa Future People music fesitval</a></h3>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<p>From 11 to 13 July 2014 at an abandoned airfield in Bolshoe Kozino village&nbsp;near Nizhny Novgorod will host a festival Alfa Future People.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><img src=\"/upload/content/Снимок4.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"197\" height=\"37\" />&nbsp;<br /><a href=\"http://www.kommersant.ru/doc/2483999\" target=\"_blank\">Dances under stars</a></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Robots, Skrillex and girls topless. Expensive \"player\" from the \"X\" Alfa-Bank.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><img src=\"/upload/content/Снимок5.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"155\" height=\"47\" />&nbsp;<br /><a href=\"http://www.kommersant.ru/doc/2483999\" target=\"_blank\">Alfa Future People on Volga river</a></h3>\r\n<p>Alfa-bank organizes electronic music festival and technologies Alfa Future People 11-13 July</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><img src=\"/upload/content/Снимок6.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"198\" height=\"28\" />&nbsp;<br /><a href=\"http://www.gazeta.ru/culture/news/2014/04/02/n_6055613.shtml\" target=\"_blank\">Alfa-bank will organize own music fetival</a></h3>\r\n<p>Alfa-bank on its official page in Facebook confirmed conduction&nbsp;festival of electronic and technologies Alfa Future People</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><img src=\"/upload/content/Снимок7.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"191\" height=\"38\" />&nbsp;<br /><a href=\"http://www.bfm.ru/news/253815?doctype=article\" target=\"_blank\">Fridman decided to conduct the main open-air in Russia</a></h3>\r\n<p>Alfa-Bank will spend advert budget on open air in Nizhniy Novgorod&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><img src=\"/upload/content/Снимок11.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"208\" height=\"26\" />&nbsp;<br /><a href=\"http://www.kommersant.ru/doc/2448778\" target=\"_blank\">Avicii and Skrilles will come to Volga</a></h3>\r\n<p>In july in Nizhniy Novgorod will be held electronic music open-air&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><img src=\"/upload/content/Снимок12.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"207\" height=\"37\" />&nbsp;<br /><a href=\"http://www.edm-news.com/2014/03/alfa-future-people.html\" target=\"_blank\">Alfa Future People, Nizhniy Novgorod, 11-13.07.14</a></h3>\r\n<p>Фестиваль пройдет с 11 по 13 июля 2014 года в Нижнем Новгороде, в поселке Большое Козино на территории заброшенного аэродрома.</p>\r\n<p>The festival will be held in Nizhniy Novgorod 11-13.07.14 in Bolshoe Kozino village on the territory of abandoned airfield</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><img src=\"/upload/content/logo1.png\" alt=\"\" /></h3>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.mtviggy.com/lists/15-best-summer-music-festivals-europe-2015/\" target=\"_blank\">The 15 Best Music Festivals in Europe this Summer</a></h3>\r\n<p>We&rsquo;ve picked 15 European summer festivals that will satisfy your hunger for intriguing newcomers and big stars.</p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><img src=\"/upload/content/clash-logo.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100\" /></h3>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://clashmusic.com/reviews/live-report-alfa-future-people-2015#view-gallery-image-1\" target=\"_blank\">Live Report: Alfa Future People 2015</a></h3>\r\nAdventures at Russia\'s biggest EDM event...\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<p><img src=\"/upload/content/logocnewssubtype.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"80\" /><br /><strong><a href=\"http://www.cnews.ru/reviews/index.shtml?2015/07/24/597912\" target=\"_blank\">Why Alfa Bank organized the biggest EDM festival</a></strong></p>\r\n<p>For the second year in a row on the Alfa Future People (AFP) - festival organized by Alfa-Bank - in addition to the hundreds of music DJs demonstrated advanced development of consumer electronics and virtual reality, the latest models of electric vehicles and blisks.</p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><img src=\"/upload/content/Снимок11.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"208\" height=\"26\" />&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.kommersant.ru/doc/2710249\" target=\"_blank\">Paul van Dyke: \"EDM as usual makes the main breakthroughs\"</a></h3>\r\nThe German Dj and producer gave an interview to \"Ъ\"</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-text\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-text\">\r\n<h3><img src=\"/upload/content/HCCPDF8P-9I.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"66\" height=\"56\" /><br /><a href=\"http://www.colta.ru/articles/music_modern/3921\" target=\"_blank\">Disco for 1million</a></h3>\r\n<p>Reportage from the festival of the future: how much does Skrillex cost and who will perfort&nbsp;&nbsp;at ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE 2015?</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-text\"><br />\r\n<h3><img src=\"/upload/content/411.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br /><a href=\"http://event.ru/news/pobediteli-premii-sobyitie-goda/\" target=\"_blank\">ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE&nbsp;was awarded as the main event of the year 2014 </a></h3>\r\n<p>ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE 2014 is the only event that has received two awards at the 3rd ceremony \"Event of the Year\": as the best musical event, and for the best technical realization.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h6>&nbsp;</h6>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>',16),
