	(3968,3,2,'<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>SPORT PLAYGROUNDS <br />AND EXTREME SHOWS<br /><img class=\"bonus safit left\" src=\"/templates/_default_/images/safit.png\" alt=\"\" /><img class=\"bonus safit right\" src=\"/templates/_default_/images/safit.png\" alt=\"\" /></h2>\r\n<div class=\"slider display-at-start inited\">\r\n<div class=\"container\" style=\"max-width: 909px;\"><img src=\"/upload/content/B42B0811.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><img style=\"display: none;\" src=\"/upload/content/B42B0939.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><img style=\"display: none;\" src=\"/upload/content/B42B1710.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><img style=\"display: none;\" src=\"/upload/content/B42B2792.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><img style=\"display: none;\" src=\"/upload/content/B42B4755.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><img style=\"display: none;\" src=\"/upload/content/DP0A4171.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></div>\r\n<input class=\"auto-slide-speed\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"5000\" /></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"block-text\">\r\n<p>In 2015 at the ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE festival there will be even more sports entertainment, spectacular shows from the &laquo;stars&raquo; of the sport, dance, yoga, trampolining master-classes, also street workouts in other sports.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Lovers of outdoor activities will be quite glad to now about 2 well-equipped football fields, six volleyball courts, 4 playgrounds for dodge ball (bouncers), streetball court and a frisbee lawn. Specially for professional American football match, a great field with spectator&rsquo;s stands will be built. July 17 two top teams &ndash; &laquo;Raiders 52&raquo; (Nizhny Novgorod) and &laquo;Rebels&raquo; (Yaroslavl) will fight for the cup of the festival. Before the match, the players will talk about the basic rules and hurls, equipment and differences between American football and rugby.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>This year, we have a great addition to the extreme zone - the real 12-meter climbing wall. You can work out with the instructor: climbing wall is equipped with ropes and safety harnesses.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>For the first time the festival will be holding a&nbsp;&nbsp; &laquo;colorful&raquo; group running race, in which can participate close to 300 AFP guests. During this unforgettable &laquo;race&raquo;, runners, generously sprinkled with colored powder from head to toe, overcome a distance of 2 km. Excellent mood, emotions and incredible festival look are guaranteed! &nbsp;<br /><br /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-text\">\r\n<div class=\"block-text\">\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>STREET WORKOUT</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp; <img src=\"/upload/content/FINAL_FINAL_VECTOR_SS_Mutant-Clan1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" />&nbsp;&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp; &nbsp;</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;\r\n<p>On the Alfa Future People festival a professional platform for street workout will be equipped!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The program includes performances of the best athletes of the Mutant Clan club (http://vk.com/mutantclan) and also street workout master classes.</p>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style=\"height: 288px;\" width=\"853\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"/upload/content/l7L0PLWSFk81.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"425\" /></td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td><img src=\"/upload/content/6-VTlRqiCr01.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"425\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>TRAMPOLINE&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><img src=\"/upload/content/2222.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" /></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The club &laquo;Up and Fly&raquo; will teach everybody, who wish to learn how to jump on the trampoline (http://upandfly.ru).</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The program includes: free jumping, performances and professional workshops.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Trampoline club &laquo;Up and Fly&raquo; is a team of professional sports instructors. For each of them sport is a calling and lifework. Their main task is to share their knowledge and experience to help all people, who wish to learn the tricks on the trampoline sports, create a beautiful and harmonious body.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"/upload/content/qAfAo5HFWBQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"425\" /></td>\r\n<td><img src=\"/upload/content/56b2a51c91cac7e20bc53503c16a2607.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"425\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>BASKETBALL</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp; &nbsp;<img src=\"/upload/content/10362812_1437767719809580_4018678338486003096_o.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"100\" />&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp; &nbsp;</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Basketball club &laquo;Nizhny Novgorod&raquo; for the second year in a row organizes a streetball playground at the festival.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The program includes: tournament with 4 professional basketball teams from Kazan, Voronezh, St. Petersburg and Nizhny Novgorod, amateur tournaments between the guests of the festival and master classes.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/upload/content/_MG_0053.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"425\" /></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/upload/content/_MG_0052.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"425\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>FRISBEE</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"/upload/content/Y6Db3YMcuTw.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" /></td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>This year we organized at the festival a special Frisbee area.</p>\r\n<p>The program includes workshops, ultimate-frisbee, disc-golf, contests and more!</p>\r\n<p>Disc-golf club from Nizhny Novgorod (<a href=\"http://www.discgolfnn.ru/\">http://www.discgolfnn.ru</a>) - it is a professional team that promotes this exciting disc-golf game in Russia. Together with the Russian Association of Disc Golf and Nizhniy Novgorod federation of sports games with a flying disc, we will hold more than 50 tournaments.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"/upload/content/6yVettMBJTA.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"425\" /></td>\r\n<td><img src=\"/upload/content/opr0EICB.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"425\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>DANCE FLOOR</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"/upload/content/Logo_Dance-Cool_var2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" /></td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Federation of sports dances DANCE COOL (http://dance-cool.ru) is the largest network of schools on street dance and contemporary dance trends, the leader in arranging the most spectacular and large-scale dance events in Nizhny Novgorod.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The program includes dance workshops from the best teachers of Federation on house dance, hip-hop dance, jazz funk. And also a special dance show performed by the DANCE-COOL CREW.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/upload/content/aFRHDfmoM7g1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/upload/content/BfGyVUzwwdk.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"425\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"/upload/content/лого.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" /></td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>In addition to the main parties, dance studio Rise is ready to offer you lots of interesting: workshops on PoleDance (vk.com/risenn) from the leading trainers of Nizhny Novgorod, bright performances on pylons, positive and explosive emotions</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>PoleDance Rise is one of the best Pole Dance studios in Nizhny Novgorod, which includes such dance styles as</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>- Pole Dance, which is a combination of choreography elements and acrobatics on the pole, is also an excellent alternative to the gym and aerobics;</p>\r\n<p>- Pole Dance Man &ndash; this is a number of complicated stunt and power elements;</p>\r\n<p>- Pole Dance Exotic is synthesis of female attractiveness, plasticity and individuality;</p>\r\n<p>- Pole Dance Kids-class is class, where kids, start from 7 years old, engaged professionally in acrobatics on the pole.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br /><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/upload/content/5OhlBvuscjE.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>AMERICAN FOOTBALL</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<p>Football is an uncompromising and tough sport, that do not leave indifferent even the most demanding audience.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>At the Alfa Future People festival you&rsquo;ll see the battle of two strongest Russian teams: the Raiders from Nizhny Novgorod and the Rebels 52 from Yaroslavl.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&laquo;Nizhny Novgorod team of American football&raquo; &laquo;Raiders 52 &raquo; (http://af52.ru) was founded in 2008 and now it is the top team in Nizhny Novgorod. Annually it takes part in various competitions:</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>in 2010 Raiders 52 won first place in the Russian Championship, in group &ldquo;B&rdquo;,</p>\r\n<p>in 2011 became the owners of the international Cup &laquo;Vytautas Magnus&raquo; (Minsk) and the winners of the regional tournament &laquo;Volga-Bowl&raquo;</p>\r\n<p>in 2013 it entered the top - 8 teams, and in 2014 the top - 4 on the basis of the Russian Championship.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The Soccer team REBELS (https://vk.com/rebels_yaroslavl) became the leading team in Yaroslavl.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The team consists of amateur athletes from other sports. The 21<sup>st</sup> of September 2013 is the day, when the team was found.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>In 2014 the team took part in a number of tournaments and has chalked up several prizes.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/upload/content/5AZVa7psFaM1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"425\" /></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/upload/content/bcvHl0efWy41.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"425\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>VOLLEYBALL</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"/upload/content/znak_GYBERNIA-b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" /></td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>On the 6 best volleyball courts the volleyball club &laquo;Gubernia&raquo; will give master classes, exhibition matches and mini-tournaments for guests of the festival.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Volleyball club &laquo;Gubernia&raquo; (https://vk.com/nnvolley) is one of the most successful sports teams in Nizhny Novgorod and the Nizhny Novgorod region.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&laquo;Gubernia&raquo; won 13 games in a row in the regular stage and took fourth place in the season, which gave the team the right to take part in the prestigious European competition, the Cup of the European Volleyball Confederation. Last year &laquo;Gubernia&raquo; made its debut on the international stage in the CEV Cup and won silver medals, and it also made success at the championship of Russia, ranking fifth line among the strongest teams of the country.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"/upload/content/010-SK1__8540A.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"425\" /></td>\r\n<td><img src=\"/upload/content/014-SK1__7302.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"425\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>FOOTBALL</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"/upload/content/logo_ФК_Волга.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>On the festival site FC &laquo;Volga&raquo; (http://www.fcvolgann.ru) organizes exciting football championship among AFP visitors. Football workshops, relay races and various competitions will be hold for festival guests.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>FC &laquo;Volga&raquo; is the main soccer team of Nizhny Novgorod and the Nizhny Novgorod region. &laquo;Volga&raquo; thrashed such top clubs as the Moscow &laquo;Spartac&raquo; (the Cup), &laquo;Dynamo&raquo; and &laquo;Locomotive&raquo;, Kazan &laquo;Rubin&raquo; and FC&nbsp; &laquo;Krasnodar&raquo; (national championship).</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>EXSTREMELAND</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"/upload/content/водный_тзнак.png\" alt=\"\" /></td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>This year, Nizhny Novgorod recreation center &laquo;Exstremeland&raquo;, special for the guests of the AFP festival, will bring a professional climbing wall and equipped playground for laser tag!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>EKSTRIMLAND is the first and only database of recreation in the Nizhny Novgorod region, where you can find all the possible entertainment for the most demanding adventurers. <a href=\"http://vk.com/extremeland\">http://vk.com/extremeland</a></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>YOGA</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<p>The first hot yoga studio on Pokrovka enabled the people of the city to join the popular in Europe and the United States the modern direction of Bikram yoga, which can rightly be called a fitness of the XXI. This year all the guests of the festival will be able to take part in our yoga trainings! You will find that yoga could give you a powerful boost of energy!</p>\r\n<br /><br /><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/upload/content/fmC-xesRaRE.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-expand\">\r\n<h3>X-FIT</h3>\r\n<div class=\"container\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"/upload/content/logo_xfit.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" /></td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Federal chain of fitness clubs X-Fit present more than 50 contemporary, thoughtful and hospitable sports clubs of premium and business class al over the country. For three hot July days, you can practice under the guidance of the best instructors from the club &laquo;X-fit Nizhny Novgorod&raquo;. Thanks to professional coaches, who will help you easily learn, how to do the exercises and calculate the load on your body! Be ensure the effectiveness of sports and recharge your batteries for the unrestrained night dance!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://xfitnn.ru/\">http://xfitnn.ru</a></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/upload/content/DP0A4150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>2014</h2>\r\n<p>In 2014, the festival Alfa Future People guests could find a sports entertainment for all tastes - and spectacular sports show on earth and the water, and the tournaments in group sports, and a variety of workshops.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Stars of extreme sports skateboarding, FMX, BMX, wakeboard, flyboard and aggressive rollers strucked the imagination of visitors with spectacular shows. The world-famous masters showed their best tricks on a specially constructed areas of obstacles and jumps in the Fun Park.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Visitors to the festival could learn extreme skateboarding, BMX, aggressive roller skating under the guidance of professional athletes and trainers, known not only in Russia but also worldwide.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The most active guests of the festival could participate in yoga master classes, street workouts, body combat, balance and jam, or try their hand at beach volleyball tournaments, basketball or aqua football.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Last year there was 12 playgrounds at the AFP festival, and anyone could rent a ball, frisbee, beach balls and other equipment.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>',19),
