	(4054,9,2,'<p>ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE 2015 starts soon and the number of questions about the&nbsp;event grows every day. Part of the answers can be found in the group Vkontakte,&nbsp;on the official website and using mobile application, but we decided to elaborate&nbsp;further one of the most important topics - cashless payment using MasterCard&nbsp;PayPass.</p>',1290),
	(4055,10,2,'<p>ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE 2015 starts soon and the number of questions about the&nbsp;event grows every day. Part of the answers can be found in the group Vkontakte,&nbsp;on the official website and using mobile application, but we decided to elaborate&nbsp;further one of the most important topics - cashless payment using MasterCard&nbsp;PayPass.</p>\r\n<p>AFP brand Manager Cristina Vdovina prepared a special video guide, from which&nbsp;you will learn all about the intricacies of the payment for food and drinks at the&nbsp;festival in one-touch and also about replenishment features of the wristlet, and as&nbsp;well about limits on your smart card.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The video is must see to master the MasterCard Paypass technology and the&nbsp;practice begins on the 17th of July!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>IMPORTANT: Keep the entire contents of the Welcome Pack kit!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><iframe style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/-Vr2Rok6KWc?rel=0\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>',1290),
	(4056,8,2,'GO PRO ON AFP',1291),
	(4057,9,2,'<p>We have already told you about the interactive GoPro brand area, but there is another surprise! Special for our guests GoPro is going to make a formal presentation of their new camera GoPro HERO4 Session. Nobody has seen it in Russia, and you will be the first to assess all its advantages. On July the 18<sup>th</sup>&nbsp;, at exactly 17:00, on the Live &amp; Bass stage you&rsquo;ll see the premiere of the smallest and coolest camera! An excellent opportunity to pump your operator skills at the master class, which will be held in the brand-area, next to the tent of technologies at 14:00.</p>',1291),
	(4058,10,2,'<p>We have already told you about the interactive GoPro brand area, but there is another surprise! Special for our guests GoPro is going to make a formal presentation of their new camera GoPro HERO4 Session. Nobody has seen it in Russia, and you will be the first to assess all its advantages. On July the 18<sup>th</sup> , at exactly 17:00, on the Live &amp; Bass stage you&rsquo;ll see the premiere of the smallest and coolest camera! An excellent opportunity to pump your operator skills at the master class, which will be held in the brand-area, next to the tent of technologies at 14:00.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>And that\'s not all! Would you like to get a camera as a gift? Take part in the Instagram contest from GoPro and win it right at the Alfa Future People festival!</p>\r\n<p>The competition starts on July the 17<sup>th</sup> , at 12:00. Terms: Subscribe to the official account GoProheroeveryone in Russia and put a photo with the hashtag #HeroAFP and the text \"Find GoPro at AFP\". Take a photo of GoPro camers, or put some footage from the GoPro shot at the festival. Find GoPro Ambassadors, discover the &nbsp;interactive zone or use your camera - make a unique frame!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Camera Crew GoPro will select the most epic photo and award three winners on July the 18<sup>th</sup> &nbsp;at 17:20 - just after the presentation of the new GoPro HERO4 The session on the Live &amp; Bass stage. The first place - camera GoPro, the second place - a certificate for free education at GoPro School, third place - a cool t-shirt from the brand.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/upload/content/hero4_session_feature_1_smallestlightest_Yuma.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>',1291),
