	(4042,9,2,'<p>Our festival has got its own hymn! The author of the hymn &laquo;Future People&raquo; is DJ Smash, and the voice belongs to the British singer Stephen Ridley. By the way, this is the second collaboration of musicians after \"The Night Is Young\" - a hit that actively storming the ratings of radio stations.</p>',1286),
	(4043,10,2,'<p>Our festival has got its own hymn! The author of the hymn &laquo;Future People&raquo; is DJ Smash, and the voice belongs to the British singer Stephen Ridley. By the way, this is the second collaboration of musicians after \"The Night Is Young\" - a hit that actively storming the ratings of radio stations.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Download, listen, and today we will announce a super competition associated with the hymn!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/alfafuturemusic\">https://soundcloud.com/alfafuturemusic</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/future-people-afp-anthem-extended/\">https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/future-people-afp-anthem-extended/</a></p>',1286),
