	(4050,8,2,'FESTIVAL OF COLORS',1289),
	(4051,9,2,'<p>We start the week with important news! Your positive reaction to the news about the colorful race has pushed us to the idea to hold at ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE festival also a Festival of Colors!</p>',1289),
	(4052,10,2,'<p>We start the week with important news! Your positive reaction to the news about the colorful race has pushed us to the idea to hold at ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE festival also a Festival of Colors!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>On 18<sup>th</sup> and 19<sup>th</sup> of July everyone will be able to take part in this epic action! Could you just imagine Live &amp; Bass scene, live music, thousands of bright young people and tons of colorful paint! This bright holiday has all chances to become the main attraction of the daily program at the AFP in 2015!</p>\r\n<p>Expect more announcements about the event! It will have no match in beautiful and vivid emotions!</p>',1289),
	(4059,8,2,'FLAT 247',1292),
	(4060,9,2,'<p>In some interviews festival organizers talked about the 5th stage at ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE, that did not go unnoticed among the most attentive members of the group. Finally, we are ready to present you another innovation in the AFP 2015 program - the dance floor FLAT247 hosted by Umaker.</p>\r\n<p>FLAT 247</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',1292),
	(4061,10,2,'<p>In some interviews festival organizers talked about the 5th stage at ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE, that did not go unnoticed among the most attentive members of the group. Finally, we are ready to present you another innovation in the AFP 2015 program - the dance floor FLAT247 hosted by Umaker.</p>\r\n<p>FLAT 247</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>FLAT 247 format is familiar to many party-goers! It is about chamber events &laquo;for friends&raquo; which are regularly broadcasted online on axe247.ru. This time, AXE, with the support of professional school of DJing and recording umaker.ru, for the first time ever, gives the unique opportunity to visit this &laquo;home party&raquo; and represents one of the most unusual in sound and concept dance floors. Retaining the innovative style of the festival with a focus on future technology and fashion trends, the scene FLAT247 hosted by UMAKER will bring together the best Russian musicians and DJs urban music style. AFP guests will be able to see more than 20 arousing passions live-performances in the styles of beatbox, scratch and live looping of the acknowledged master of the genre.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>In the daytime there will be lots of contests with prizes from AXE and UMAKER, training sessions for DJing and scratching, drawing of certificates for studing in the school, and much more in the same strain! Technical partner of this dance floor lighting solutions MIXPRODUCTION will surprise you bright video installations and powerful sound in style of FLAT247. Meet the future and the present of Russian beatbox, scratch and live looping scene:</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>AGRABA / ANTENTION / ARTUR / ASAGA / AZYSTUFF / DIMA DEM / DMNDZ / ENZY / ERIK / FANKFORMER / KRAZYRAF / LEKS / MASTER MARIO / MITYA / НАСТЯ МАСЛОВА / RE-PAC / STEPPA STYLE / SYNOPTIX.*</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>* Names are listed in alphabetical order.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Detailed information about the artists at the festival is on the website in the section LINE-UP - <a href=\"/ru/lineup2015.html\">http://alfafuture.com/ru/lineup2015.html</a> and online <a href=\"http://www.axefuture.ru\">www.axefuture.ru</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/upload/content/facebook_AFR_2_копия.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>',1292),
	(4062,8,2,'CONSTRUCTION AT AFP 2015',1293),
	(4063,9,2,'<p>We have prepared a small photo report from the construction site of the festival ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE for all guests of the festival. Construction is on schedule! Shooting date - 07/07/2015</p>',1293),
	(4064,10,2,'<p style=\"text-align: left;\">We have prepared a small photo report from the construction site of the festival ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE for all guests of the festival. Construction is on schedule! Shooting date - 07/07/2015</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/upload/content/1kzwWakq6gw.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/upload/content/4MAepSUJh1U.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/upload/content/4QiOKJ82tO4.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/upload/content/Im9mpQGAMrc.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/upload/content/vi1kESPBfEM.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/upload/content/DQmf17qN8rM.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/upload/content/F1KnmvZhzFQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/upload/content/oXjQIIj2DVE.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/upload/content/K2hOijstxwY.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/upload/content/4IrSfrrcMSY1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>',1293),
