	(4112,8,2,'GOOGLE AT AFP',1295),
	(4113,9,2,'<p>Google and Anton Chekhov Moscow Art Theatre present a project &laquo;Chekhov Alive&raquo; at the Alfa Future People!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>500 readers, 24 hours, people from different parts of the world will meet live on YouTube, to take part in the dramatized readings &laquo;Chekhov\'s alive&raquo; online. And you can become one of them!</p>',1295),
	(4114,10,2,'<p>Google and Anton Chekhov Moscow Art Theatre present a project &laquo;Chekhov Alive&raquo; at the Alfa Future People!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>500 readers, 24 hours, people from different parts of the world will meet live on YouTube, to take part in the dramatized readings &laquo;Chekhov\'s alive&raquo; online. And you can become one of them!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>To learn who you are from Chekhov\'s characters: the eternal student, careerist, altruist or sweet sinner, you can right at the festival. And you also can charge your smartphone, relax with a book, to apply for participation in the readings and get a nice surprise from the project!</p>\r\n<p>Join us on g.co/Chekhov</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/upload/content/FOT_9134.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" /></p>',1295),
	(4115,8,2,'THE IRON THRONE',1296),
	(4116,9,2,'<p>The Iron Throne of Westeros will arrive to the festival! In a special zone arranged by ??the online service Amediateka, the real Iron Throne, that belongs to the King of the Andals and the First Men from &laquo;Game of Thrones&raquo; will be waiting for everyone!</p>',1296),
	(4117,10,2,'<p>Friends, we have another exiting piece of news! The Iron Throne of Westeros will arrive to the festival! In a special zone arranged by ??the online service Amediateka, the real Iron Throne, that belongs to the King of the Andals and the First Men from &laquo;Game of Thrones&raquo; will be waiting for everyone!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>To admire this legendary creature can anyone and as for the fans of legal and high quality Internet content, they will have a special privilege. Just show on your phone or tablet any of officially bought game, audio or subscription to an online resource or a mobile application and the throne of the ruler of the Seven Kingdoms will be at your disposal!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/upload/content/tron1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" /></p>',1296),
