	(5893,10,2,'<p align=\"left\">The ceremony of awarding the winners of The European Best Event Awards (EuBea) was held in Sevilla, Spain.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">EuBea - one of the biggest international competitions in the field of event-industry and communications. For the first one of the nominations won by representatives of Russia: the festival of electronic music and technology Alfa Future People was named best musical event of the year in Europe.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">The best event of the year was named the celebration of the bicentenary of the Battle of Waterloo, which brought together more than 100 000 participants. Reconstruction of the famous battle lasted three days and cost the organizers of the 5 million euros.<br />EuBea Prize awarded in 19 categories. The jury selects the best: sporting events, conferences, social initiative, musical event, festival, public event, and corporate events, such as the best team building. Separately awarded prize for the best event of the year. In some categories (including the final) mark the three winners - winners of the first, second and third places.<br />Shortlist EuBea formed on the results of online voting, the winner is determined by a jury of thirty industry professionals. Ranked Among them are the heads of advertising agencies and marketing director of the directions of the largest companies in the world. Key evaluation criteria are creativity, economic efficiency of the project, technical training, venue, media coverage and general management activities.</p>\r\n<p align=\"\">&nbsp;</p>',1308),
	(5894,8,2,'Alfa Future People the best music fectival according KudaGo',1309),
	(5895,9,2,'<p>November 16 in Moscow hosted the award KudaGo, where Alfa Future People was declared the best music festival of the year.</p>',1309),
	(5896,10,2,'<p>How to understand where are the best events of the city, where to spend time with benefit and pleasure? Who deserves the credit of trust from visitors? The answer to these questions came to be known at the end of November 2015 at the awards ceremony Award KudaGo.</p>\r\n<p>Over 2 months every visitor Prize noted he liked the place and the developments in the 30 nominations. Then, the case took the invited experts, whose evaluation is also affected by the outcome of the struggle.&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;The jury consisted of media persons, including journalists, singers, presenters and musicians. All of them are often directly involved in the activities taking place in the capital, so they think you can trust. The final word was for Sati Casanova, Nikas Safronov, Jana Chourikova, NOIZE MC and other famous personalities.<br />&nbsp;<br />Applications for participation in the Award submitted more than 400 candidates, including Park Arts \"Museon\" festival \"Circle of Light\", the exhibition \"The Great Impressionists\' club YOTASPACE and others. Total allocated 30 nominations. Awards received: best urban music and gastronomic festivals, the best park and exhibition space, the best creative cluster, the best Fair, and other events and locations. For a complete list of nominations, you can on the official site of the award (<a href=\"http://award.kudago.com/\">http://award.kudago.com/</a>) The award ceremony took place on November 16 in the Central House of Artists.</p>',1309),
