	(5914,10,2,'<p>We are happy to announce the long-awaited news - &nbsp;the date of the festival! ALFA FUTURE PEOPLE will be held from 22-24 July 2016</p>\r\n<p>We recommend that you do not put off buying tickets until the last moment and take them now - then they will only be more expensive. And note, this year to buy more correct and profitable on our site.</p>\r\n<p>Before the most memorable weekends of the coming year remained 7 months. Get Yoda wisdom and start planning now!</p>',1313),
	(5926,10,2,'<p>Lost Frequencies - dj project of belgian producer Felix De Laet. His name and music started to buzz around the world in October 2014 with the smash hit Are You With Me, rework of Easton Corbin song.&nbsp;<br />In 2015 singles Are You With Me and Reality topped all European music charts. We are happily waiting Lost Frequencies to play at Alfa Future People Festival 2016!&nbsp;</p>',1317),
